Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,西贡\N{\rEng}Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是在西贡\N{\rEng}I'm still only in Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,每次醒来  总以为重返森林\N{\rEng}Every time, I think I'm gonna wake up back in thejungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次回家时  情况最糟\N{\rEng}When I was home after my first tour, it was worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,醒来后  发觉只是噩梦一场\N{\rEng}I'd wake up, and there'd be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎没和妻子说话\N{\rEng}I hardly said a word to my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,直到答应离婚才说了个  是\N{\rEng}until I said yes to a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当我在战场时  很想回家\N{\rEng}When I was here, I wanted to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当我在家\N{\rEng}When I was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,又想着回到森林\N{\rEng}all I could think of was getting backinto thejungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我已回来一星期了\N{\rEng}I'm here a weeknow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,等待任务\N{\rEng}Waiting for a mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,意志消沉\N{\rEng}getting softer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我留在房间越久  只会越软弱\N{\rEng}Every minute I stay in this room, I get weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,越共留在森林越久\N{\rEng}And every minute Charlie squats in the bush,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就越强悍\N{\rEng}he gets stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,每次环顾四周\N{\rEng}Each time I looked around,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,墙壁似乎分秒迫近\N{\rEng}the walls moved in a little tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都有愿望\N{\rEng}Everyone gets everything he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我渴望任务\N{\rEng}I wanted a mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是咎由自取  他们给了我一个\N{\rEng}and for my sins, they gave me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,像客房服务般交给了我\N{\rEng}Brought it up to me like room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,威尔德上尉  你在吗？\N{\rEng}Captain Willard? Are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在！ 我就来\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是项艰巨的任务\N{\rEng}It was a real choice mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,当完成它后\N{\rEng}And when it was over,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不想再有第二个\N{\rEng}I'd never want another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有何贵干？\N{\rEng}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧  上尉\N{\rEng}Are you all right, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我像有事吗？\N{\rEng}What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是威尔德上尉吗？ 505营？  -没错\N{\rEng}-Are you Willard, 505th Battalion?  -AffiIrmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-第173空降部队？  -是的\N{\rEng}-1 73rd Airborne?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-隶属特种部队？  -把门关上！\N{\rEng}-Assigned to SOG?  -Hey, buddy, gonna shut the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们奉命送你去机场\N{\rEng}We have orders to escort you to the airfiIeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么罪名？\N{\rEng}What are the charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-我犯了什么事？  -你没犯事  上尉\N{\rEng}-What'd I do?  -There's no charges, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让你向老川的情报处报到\N{\rEng}You have orders to report to Com-Sec Intelligence at Nha Trang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,－你看  －没错吧！\N{\rEng}-I see.  -All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-派我去老川？  -是的\N{\rEng}-Nha Trang, for me?  -That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉  你有几个小时收拾行李\N{\rEng}Come on, Captain. You still have a few hours to get cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不太舒服  -上尉？\N{\rEng}-I'm not feeling too good.  -Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫  过来帮把手  他烂醉如泥\N{\rEng}Dave, come here and give me a hand. We got a dead one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  上尉  冲个凉\N{\rEng}Come on, Captain. Let's take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-别乱来  -扶稳他\N{\rEng}-Don't be an ass.  -Get a hold of him good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们帮你冲凉  上尉\N{\rEng}We're gonna take a shower, Captain. In we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,站在这下面  上尉\N{\rEng}Stand underneath this, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去世上最凶险的地方\N{\rEng}I was going to the worst place in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,当时却一无所知\N{\rEng}and I didn't even know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,花数星期  逆流而上数百公里\N{\rEng}Weeks away and hundreds of miles up a river...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在战火中迂回前行  就像一条主电缆\N{\rEng}that snaked through the war like a main circuit cable...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,直插向库尔兹\N{\rEng}plugged straight into kurtz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上校的回忆录传到我手上\N{\rEng}It was no accident that I got to be the caretaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,绝非偶然\N{\rEng}of Colonel Walter E. kurtz's memory--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我回到西贡一样\N{\rEng}any more than being back in Saigon was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他的故事  有一部份关于我\N{\rEng}There is no way to tell his story without telling my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,若他的故事是真实告白\N{\rEng}If his story is really a confession--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,威尔德上尉报到  长官\N{\rEng}Captain Willard reporting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的也是\N{\rEng}then so is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-上尉  很好  进来吧  -谢谢  长官\N{\rEng}-Captain. Good. Come on in.  -Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,稍息\N{\rEng}Stand at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,将军\N{\rEng}General.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,抽烟吗？\N{\rEng}You want a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不了  谢谢  长官\N{\rEng}No, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉  你以前见过这位先生吗？\N{\rEng}Have you ever seen this man before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有  -见过将军或我吗？\N{\rEng}-No, sir.  -Met the general or myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,从未私下会面  长官\N{\rEng}No, sir.Not personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你经常单独行动  是吗？\N{\rEng}You've worked a lot on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,报告上说你擅长  情报工作和反间谍\N{\rEng}Your report specifiIes intelligence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,替情报一处工作\N{\rEng}counterintelligence with Com-Sec, ''I'' Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能透露行动内容\N{\rEng}I'm not presently disposed to discuss those operations, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你在情报一处  不是为中情局效力吗？\N{\rEng}Did you not work for the CIA in ''I'' Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  长官\N{\rEng}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你没于1968年6月18日\N{\rEng}Did you not assassinate a government tax collector...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在广储县暗杀政府税务人员吗？\N{\rEng}Quang Tri Province, June 1 8, 1 968?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉？\N{\rEng}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  我不知道任何类似事件或行动\N{\rEng}Sir, I am unaware of any such activity or operation--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就算知道  也不能透露\N{\rEng}nor would I be disposed to discuss such an operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有关行动的一切  长官\N{\rEng}if it did, in fact, exist, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们边吃边谈吧\N{\rEng}I thought we'd have a bite of lunch while we talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你胃口好  上尉\N{\rEng}I hope you brought a good appetite, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我注意到  你一只手不方便\N{\rEng}I notice that you have a bad hand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤了？\N{\rEng}You wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,休假时钓鱼弄伤的  长官\N{\rEng}I had a little fiIshing accident on R and R, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-休假时去钓鱼？  -是的  长官\N{\rEng}-Fishing on R and R?  -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,身体好了吗？  准备好执行任务了？\N{\rEng}But you're feeling fiIt? You're ready for duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  将军  准备好了\N{\rEng}Yes, General. Very much so, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看看有什么  烧牛肉\N{\rEng}Well, let's see what we have here, roast beef,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,通常还不错\N{\rEng}and usually it's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吃看  杰瑞  传一下\N{\rEng}Try some,Jerry, and pass it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,两边一起传  省点时间\N{\rEng}To save a little time, we might pass both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉  吃这虾吗？\N{\rEng}Captain, I don't know how you feel about this shrimp...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,若你吃下\N{\rEng}but if you'll eat it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,足见你胆识过人\N{\rEng}you'll never have to prove your courage in any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要一块\N{\rEng}I swear, why don't I just take a piece here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉  你听说过沃特库尔兹上校吗？\N{\rEng}Captain, you've heard of Colonel Walter E. kurtz?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我听过这名字\N{\rEng}Yes, sir, I've heard the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,天呀！\N{\rEng}Oh,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,第五特种部队作战指挥\N{\rEng}Operations offiIcer, Fifth Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克  放录音带给上尉听\N{\rEng}Luke, would you play that tape for the captain, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-好的  长官  -仔细听  上尉\N{\rEng}-Yes, sir. I'm sorry, sir.  -Listen to this carefully, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,10月9日  4：30  防区彼得  域陀  阿甘\N{\rEng}October 6, 0430 hours, sector Peter, Victor, king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在柬埔寨监听到的\N{\rEng}These were monitored out of Cambodia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,证实是库上校的声音\N{\rEng}This has been verifiIed as Col. kurtz's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见一只蜗牛\N{\rEng}I watched a snail...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爬在剃刀边缘\N{\rEng}crawl along the edge of a straight razor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的梦\N{\rEng}That's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,噩梦\N{\rEng}That's my nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爬动  滑行\N{\rEng}Crawling, slithering...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在剃刀\N{\rEng}along the edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,边缘\N{\rEng}of a straight razor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,活生生的\N{\rEng}and surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,接收编号11  68年12月30日  5时\N{\rEng}Transmission 1 1, received '68, December 30, 0500 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,防区阿甘  祖路  阿甘\N{\rEng}Sector king, Zulu, king.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们必须杀死它们\N{\rEng}But we must kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,把它们烧成灰\N{\rEng}We must incinerate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一只接一只的猪\N{\rEng}Pig after pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一只接一只的牛\N{\rEng}Cow after cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一个接一个的村庄  一支接一支的军队\N{\rEng}Village after village. Army after army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们称我是杀手\N{\rEng}And they call me an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是五十步笑百步\N{\rEng}What do you call it when the assassins accuse the assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说谎\N{\rEng}They lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说谎  而我们对说谎者\N{\rEng}They lie, and we have to be merciful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还得仁慈\N{\rEng}for those who lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那些个富豪\N{\rEng}Those nabobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌他们\N{\rEng}I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我很讨厌他们\N{\rEng}I do hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特库尔兹  是本国培育出的\N{\rEng}Walt kurtz was one of the most outstanding offiIcers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,最优秀的军官之一\N{\rEng}this country's ever produced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在各方面都出类拔萃\N{\rEng}He was brilliant. He was outstanding in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,人品也很好  有人道精神\N{\rEng}And he was a good man, too, a humanitarian man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明  幽默\N{\rEng}A man of wit and humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他加入了特种部队\N{\rEng}He joined the Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,此后\N{\rEng}And after that his...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他的想法  行事\N{\rEng}ideas, methods...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,变得\N{\rEng}became...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,反常\N{\rEng}unsound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,反常\N{\rEng}Unsound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  他率领越南山民军\N{\rEng}Now he's crossed into Cambodia with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,越境进入柬埔寨  他们敬他若神明\N{\rEng}Montagnard army of his that worship the man like a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,连极荒谬的命令也奉行\N{\rEng}and follow every order, however ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有更惊人的消息要告诉你\N{\rEng}Well, I have some other shocking news to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,库上校将因谋杀\N{\rEng}Col. kurtz was about to be arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而被捕\N{\rEng}for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白  长官  他杀了谁？\N{\rEng}I don't follow, sir. Murdered who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,库尔兹下令处决了  几名越南情报员\N{\rEng}kurtz had ordered the execution of some Vietnamese intelligence agents--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,认为他们是双重间谍\N{\rEng}men he believed were double agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他独断专行\N{\rEng}So he took matters into his own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧  威尔德\N{\rEng}Well, you see, Willard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这场战役\N{\rEng}in this war,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是非难辨\N{\rEng}things get confused out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,包括权力  理想  旧道德观\N{\rEng}Power, ideals, the old morality...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,以及实际的军事需要\N{\rEng}and practical military necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但在那和当地人一起\N{\rEng}But out there with these natives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,被敬为神明\N{\rEng}it must be a temptation to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很是诱人\N{\rEng}be God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为任何人的心中  必有冲突\N{\rEng}Because there's a conflict in every human heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在理性和非理性间\N{\rEng}between the rational and the irrational...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,善与恶间\N{\rEng}between good and evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,善不一定总战胜恶\N{\rEng}and good does not always triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有时\N{\rEng}Sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,林肯说的  善良天使\N{\rEng}the dark side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,会被邪恶击败\N{\rEng}overcomes what Lincoln called the better angels of our nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都有临界点\N{\rEng}Every man has got a breaking point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我也一样\N{\rEng}You and I have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,库尔兹已到了他的\N{\rEng}Walt kurtz has reached his.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显  他已疯了\N{\rEng}And very obviously, he has gone insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  长官  显然是疯了\N{\rEng}Yes, sir. Very much so, sir. Obviously insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的任务是乘海军巡逻艇  沿着湄南河\N{\rEng}Your mission is to proceed up the Nung River in a navy patrol boat--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻库上校的踪迹\N{\rEng}pick up Col. kurtz's path at Nu Mung Ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着它  沿路收集情报\N{\rEng}follow it, learn what you can along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当你发现上校  用一切手段\N{\rEng}When you fiInd the colonel, infiIltrate his team by--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,渗入他的组织\N{\rEng}whatever means available
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,终结上校的指挥\N{\rEng}and terminate the colonel's command.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,处决上校\N{\rEng}Terminate the colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那里为所欲为\N{\rEng}He's out there operating without any decent restraint...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,做出不可饶恕的\N{\rEng}totally beyond the pale of any acceptable...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,行径\N{\rEng}human conduct...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而他仍握有军权\N{\rEng}and he is still on the fiIeld, commanding troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,执行军纪  处决他\N{\rEng}Terminate with extreme prejudice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要明白  上尉  这任务从不存在\N{\rEng}You understand, Captain, that this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会记录在案\N{\rEng}does not exist nor will it ever exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀过多少人？\N{\rEng}How many people had I already killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我能肯定的有6个\N{\rEng}There were those six that I knew about for sure--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都死在我跟前\N{\rEng}close enough to blow their last breath in my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次我要杀同胞\N{\rEng}But this time it was an American...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是个军官\N{\rEng}and an officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说  应该没什么分别\N{\rEng}That wasn't supposed to make any difference to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上却不好受\N{\rEng}but it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在战场上指控人谋杀\N{\rEng}Charging a man with murder in this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就像在  印第500车上  开超速罚单\N{\rEng}was like handing out speeding tickets at the Indy 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受了任务\N{\rEng}I took the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能怎么办？\N{\rEng}What the hell else was I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但我真的不知道  找到了他会怎样做\N{\rEng}But I really didn't know what I'd do when I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你查过油箱吗？\N{\rEng}Did you check the tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我乘海军巡逻艇  沿着岸边而行\N{\rEng}I was being ferried down the coast in a navy PBR...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是种橡皮巡逻艇\N{\rEng}a type of plastic patrol boat--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在河上随处可见\N{\rEng}a pretty common sight on the rivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说用来搜集情报\N{\rEng}They said it was a good way to pick up information and move...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不会引人注目  这样不错\N{\rEng}without drawing a lot of attention, and that was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我需要新鲜空气和时间\N{\rEng}I needed the air and the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的问题是  我并非独自一人\N{\rEng}Only problem was I wouldn't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,早安  上尉\N{\rEng}Mornin', Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,船员绝大多数是新手\N{\rEng}The crew were mostly just kids--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爱唱摇滚乐  不知大难临头\N{\rEng}rockand rollers with one foot in their graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-你多大？  -17\N{\rEng}-How old are you?  -Seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,叫大厨的机械师\N{\rEng}The machinist--the one they called Chef--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来自新奥尔良\N{\rEng}was from New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他太紧张  不该来越南\N{\rEng}He was wrapped too tight for Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,或许去新奥尔良也如此\N{\rEng}Probably wrapped too tight for New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  开50口径机枪  是洛杉矶南部海滩\N{\rEng}Lance, on the forward fifties...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一位著名的冲浪高手\N{\rEng}was a famous surfer from the beaches south of L.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看他一眼\N{\rEng}To look at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就知他这辈子没开过枪\N{\rEng}you wouldn't believe he'd ever fired a weapon in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,克林先生  出身纽约南布朗克斯贫民区\N{\rEng}Clean--Mr. Clean--was from some South Bronx shit-hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想越南的阳光和环境\N{\rEng}and I think the light and the space of Vietnam...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,的确令他清醒不少\N{\rEng}really put the zap on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  酋长  菲腊\N{\rEng}Then there was Phillips, the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这也许是我的任务\N{\rEng}It might have been my mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但船却由菲腊掌控\N{\rEng}but it sure as shit was the chief''s boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有两处的水深够\N{\rEng}There's about two points where we can draw enough water...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可进入湄南河\N{\rEng}to get into the Nung River.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但都很危险  是越共的地盘\N{\rEng}They're both hot. Belong to Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\rEng}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别抽烟\N{\rEng}Don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这参加过几次特别行动\N{\rEng}You know, I've pulled a few special ops in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大约半年前\N{\rEng}About six months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我带一个人穿过都朗桥\N{\rEng}I took a man who was going up past the bridge at Do Lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是正规军\N{\rEng}He was regular army too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听说他已吞枪自尽\N{\rEng}Heard he shot himself in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,起初  我认为他们给错了档案\N{\rEng}At first I thought they handed me the wrong dossier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信  他们想取这人的性命\N{\rEng}I couldn't believe they wanted this man dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,三代均出身西点  尖子生\N{\rEng}Third-generation West Point, top of his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,韩战  空降兵  获勋章无数\N{\rEng}korea, Airborne, about a thousand decorations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,诸如此类的\N{\rEng}Et cetera, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到带子上他的声音  很感兴趣\N{\rEng}I'd heard his voice on the tape, and it really put the hookin me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但无法把它和这人联系起来\N{\rEng}but I couldn't connect up that voice with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正如他们所说  他战功卓著\N{\rEng}Like they said, he had an impressive career.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,或许太卓越了\N{\rEng}Maybe too impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是完美\N{\rEng}I mean, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾被推荐出任要职\N{\rEng}He was being groomed for one of the top slots in the corporation--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,将军  参谋长  等等\N{\rEng}general, chief of staff, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,1964年\N{\rEng}In 1 664,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他陪顾问官巡视越南后回国\N{\rEng}he returned from a tour with Advisory Command in Vietnam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎开始走下坡\N{\rEng}and things started to slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他交给参谋长联席会议\N{\rEng}His report to the Joint Chiefs of Staff
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,及约翰逊总统的报告被压\N{\rEng}and Lyndon Johnson was restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们似乎并不欣赏他的见解\N{\rEng}Seems they didn't dig what he had to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,此后的几个月  他3次申请\N{\rEng}During the next few months, he made three requests for transfer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,转住佐治压州班宁堡接受空降训练\N{\rEng}to Airborne training, Fort Benning, Georgia,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,最终获批\N{\rEng}and was finally accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,空降兵？\N{\rEng}Airborne?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当时他已38岁\N{\rEng}He was 38 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他究竟打的什么主意？\N{\rEng}Why the fuck would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,1966年  加入特种部队\N{\rEng}1966, joins Special Forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.12,0:24:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,重回越南\N{\rEng}returns to Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\rEng}Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.44,0:24:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-弧光行动  -怎么了？\N{\rEng}-Arc light.  -What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-B-52轰炸  -什么？\N{\rEng}-B-52 strike.  -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.15,0:24:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是什么？  -弧光\N{\rEng}-What's that?  -Arc light.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.55,0:24:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真讨厌  每次听到\N{\rEng}I hate that. Every time I hear that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都没好事\N{\rEng}something terrible happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,越共一点也不在乎\N{\rEng}Charlie don't never see 'em or hear 'em, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了\N{\rEng}There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.96,0:24:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,冲击力让人呼吸困难\N{\rEng}Concussion will suck the air out of your damn lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有可怕的事要发生\N{\rEng}Something terrible is gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.70,0:24:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有烟！\N{\rEng}Smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.23,0:24:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是二次燃烧\N{\rEng}Secondary burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.50,0:24:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是休伊直升机  有很多架\N{\rEng}Hueys over there. Lots of Hueys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看  酋长\N{\rEng}Let's have a look, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.04,0:24:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是空中骑兵  九团一队\N{\rEng}It was the Air-Cav. First of the Ninth
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.87,0:24:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们\N{\rEng}That's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,负责护送我们到湄南河口\N{\rEng}our escorts to the mouth of the Nung River.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.68,0:24:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们应该\N{\rEng}But they were supposed to be waiting for us
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在前方30公里处等啊\N{\rEng}another 30 kilometers ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.65,0:24:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,空中机动部队  就是没法安生\N{\rEng}Well, Air Mobile. Those boys just couldn't stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.47,0:25:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  下来\N{\rEng}Hey, kid, come on. Get down. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.15,0:25:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,九团一队  以前是支骑兵部队\N{\rEng}First of the Ninth was an old cavalry division...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.48,0:25:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,卖了马  换成直升机\N{\rEng}that had cashed in its horses for choppers...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,专在湄南河一带搜敌\N{\rEng}and gone tear-assing around 'Nam looking for the shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好几次令越共措手不及\N{\rEng}They'd given Charlie a few surprises in their time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.23,0:25:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们这次突袭\N{\rEng}What they were mopping up now
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.60,0:25:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时前毫无征兆\N{\rEng}hadn't even happened yet an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.43,0:25:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,继续跑  我们在拍电视\N{\rEng}Just keeping running by. We're for television.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别看镜头  继续  快走\N{\rEng}Don't look at the camera. Just keep--Go on. keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.04,0:25:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在拍电视  别看镜头\N{\rEng}This is for television. Don't look at the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.77,0:25:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,作战斗状  前进\N{\rEng}Just go by like you're fiIghting, like you're fiIghting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.48,0:25:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,别看镜头  在拍电视\N{\rEng}Don't look at the camera. It's for television.Just go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快走！ 前进\N{\rEng}Just go by. keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.28,0:25:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别看镜头  走啊\N{\rEng}keep going. Don't look at the camera. Go on. keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.20,0:26:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  快走\N{\rEng}All right, come on. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.68,0:26:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对.这边\N{\rEng}Right here. Yes. Over here. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.14,0:26:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥官在哪？\N{\rEng}Where can I fiInd the CO?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.24,0:26:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,上校正准备降落！\N{\rEng}That's the colonel comin' down!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.09,0:26:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥官在直升机上\N{\rEng}The CO's on that chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.03,0:27:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉  沿后面那条约90米远的林木线轰炸\N{\rEng}Lieutenant, bomb that tree line back about 1 00 yards!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.40,0:27:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-给我点呼吸的空间  -是  长官\N{\rEng}-Give me some room to breathe!  -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.91,0:27:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-死亡扑克  -什么  长官？\N{\rEng}Body cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.98,0:27:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-带上死亡扑克  -是  长官\N{\rEng}-Bring my body cards!  -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.03,0:27:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在找坦克吗？ 有5辆坏的\N{\rEng}I'm the Fourth Tank commander. I got fiIve tanks broken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.64,0:27:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你说够了  上尉\N{\rEng}We're all right with the tanks. It's all right, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.17,0:27:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是威尔德上尉！\N{\rEng}Captain Willard!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.68,0:27:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我有情报二处的优先文件\N{\rEng}I carry priority papers from Com-Sec Intelligence, II Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.21,0:27:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,相信老川已通知你\N{\rEng}I understand Nha Trang has briefed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.31,0:27:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,支援我的任务\N{\rEng}on the requirements of my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.05,0:27:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么任务？  老川没消息来\N{\rEng}What mission? I haven't heard from Nha Trang.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.68,0:27:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  你的部队应护送我们进湄南河\N{\rEng}Sir, your unit is supposed to escort us into the Nung!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.72,0:27:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-再安排吧  -上校\N{\rEng}-We'll see what we can do.  -Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.29,0:27:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让开  上尉  我要办正事\N{\rEng}But just stay out of my way until this is done, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.26,0:27:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看看有些什么人\N{\rEng}All right, let's see what we have. Let's see what we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.08,0:27:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,黑桃二  黑桃三  方块四\N{\rEng}A two of spades, three of spades, four of diamonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.49,0:28:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,梅花六  黑桃八\N{\rEng}six of clubs, eight of spades.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.99,0:28:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人不配给J\N{\rEng}There isn't one worth a jack in the whole bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.80,0:28:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,方块四\N{\rEng}Four of diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.43,0:28:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-上尉  那是什么？  -死亡牌！\N{\rEng}-Hey, Captain, what's that?  -Death cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.70,0:28:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么？  -死亡牌\N{\rEng}-What?  -Death cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.44,0:28:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-死亡？  -让越共知道是谁干的\N{\rEng}-Death?  -Lets Charlie know who did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.01,0:28:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-振作点  小子  -我们不会伤害你\N{\rEng}-Cheer up, son.  -We will not hurt or harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.48,0:28:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-卧倒！ -卧倒！\N{\rEng}-Fire in the hole!  -Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.40,0:28:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方被越共和北越人控制\N{\rEng}This is an area that is controlled by the Vietcong and North Vietnamese.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.51,0:28:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.58,0:28:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来帮你们\N{\rEng}We are here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.67,0:28:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你们\N{\rEng}We extend a welcome hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.54,0:28:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-快点  都进去了吗？  -愿意重投\N{\rEng}-Come on. Everybody in?  -to those who would like to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.77,0:28:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,南越政府的人\N{\rEng}to the arms of the South Vietnamese government.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.25,0:28:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,进去  快点！\N{\rEng}Get in. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.38,0:29:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-走吧！ -这地方被\N{\rEng}-Move it out.  -This is an area that is controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.29,0:29:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,越共和北越人控制\N{\rEng}by the Vietcong and North Vietnamese.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.46,0:29:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！ 怎么了？\N{\rEng}Hey! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.96,0:29:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.93,0:29:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙受了重伤  长官\N{\rEng}This man's hurt pretty bad, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.20,0:29:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他用壶盖掩着肚肠\N{\rEng}About the only thing that's holding his guts in, sir, is that pot lid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.70,0:29:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？ 你要说什么？\N{\rEng}Yeah? What do you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.34,0:29:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他是可恶的越共\N{\rEng}This soldier is dirty VC.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.74,0:29:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他想喝水  让他喝田里的水吧\N{\rEng}He wants water. He can drink paddy water.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.21,0:29:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开！  给我  给我水壶\N{\rEng}Get outta here! Give me that canteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.79,0:29:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是越共    -任何勇敢作战的人\N{\rEng}-He's VC!  -Any man that's brave enough to--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.76,0:29:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开！  我会踹你的屁股！\N{\rEng}Get outta here! I'll kick your fuckin' ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.50,0:29:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀了我们很多人！\N{\rEng}He killed a lot of our people!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.37,0:29:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,任何勇敢作战  置性命于不顾的人\N{\rEng}Any man brave enough to fiIght with his guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.27,0:29:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,随时都可喝我的水\N{\rEng}strapped on him can drink from my canteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.14,0:29:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,上校  我想有个水手\N{\rEng}Hey, Colonel, I think one of those sailors
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.92,0:29:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是冲浪手兰斯约翰逊\N{\rEng}is Lance Johnson, the surfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.91,0:29:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪？  这里吗？  你肯定？\N{\rEng}Where? Here? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.38,0:29:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\rEng}Yeah? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.38,0:29:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,去找他\N{\rEng}Down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.32,0:29:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,重覆  我们统计了死者\N{\rEng}Repeat. We have a body count. We have--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.32,0:30:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么  水手？\N{\rEng}What's your name, sailor?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.09,0:30:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,三等枪手兰斯约翰逊  长官\N{\rEng}-Gunner's Mate Third Class Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.03,0:30:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,三等枪手\N{\rEng}Gunner's Mate Third Class
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.64,0:30:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  是冲浪手兰斯约翰逊吗？\N{\rEng}Lance Johnson, the surfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.46,0:30:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.23,0:30:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很荣幸见到你  兰斯\N{\rEng}It's an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.00,0:30:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我钦佩你的板尖冲浪有好几年了\N{\rEng}I've admired your nose riding for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.33,0:30:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还有急转\N{\rEng}I like your cutback too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.78,0:30:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无人能比！\N{\rEng}I think you have the best cutback there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢  长官  -不用叫我长官  兰斯\N{\rEng}-Thank you, sir.  -You can cut out the ''sir'' crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.21,0:30:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我比尔基尔戈  我喜欢右脚在前\N{\rEng}I'm Bill kilgore. I'm a goofy foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.34,0:30:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-他跟你一起的？  -是的\N{\rEng}-This guy with ya?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.44,0:30:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想给你介绍几个人\N{\rEng}I want you to meet some guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.35,0:30:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-迈克  来自圣地压哥  -很远\N{\rEng}-This is Mike from San Diego.  -Far out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.35,0:30:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,钟尼  来自马里布\N{\rEng}Johnny from Malibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.58,0:30:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗨  钟尼  -冲浪高手\N{\rEng}-John, hi. Far out.  -Solid surfers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.12,0:30:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没人赶得上你\N{\rEng}None of us are anywhere near your class though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.85,0:30:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,过奖了\N{\rEng}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.02,0:30:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们经常在附近冲浪  兰斯\N{\rEng}We do a lot of surfiIng around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.92,0:30:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望尽早完成行动\N{\rEng}I like to fiInish operations early.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.96,0:30:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,飞去维杜冲浪\N{\rEng}Fly down to Yung Tau for the evening glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.66,0:30:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,来这后  一直在哪冲浪  兰斯？\N{\rEng}Been riding since you got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.16,0:30:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  来后没冲过浪\N{\rEng}No way. I haven't surfed since I been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.87,0:30:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,以主耶稣基督  带来善行\N{\rEng}Through Christ, our Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.97,0:30:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,以基督和圣灵\N{\rEng}from Whom all good things come...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.01,0:30:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,光明荣耀归全能天父\N{\rEng}through Him in the unity of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.18,0:30:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-阿门  -我们祈祷  对天父怀有信心\N{\rEng}All glory and honor is Yours, Almighty Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.28,0:30:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,依着救世主的话\N{\rEng}Let us bring our iniquities to the Father in the words our Savior gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.75,0:31:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在天上的父\N{\rEng}Our Father, Who art in heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.17,0:31:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,愿你的名被尊为圣（《马太福音》6：9）\N{\rEng}hallowed be Thy name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.79,0:31:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,愿你的国降临\N{\rEng}Thy kingdom come.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.39,0:31:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,愿你的旨意成就在地上  如同在天上一样\N{\rEng}Thy will be done on earth as it is in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.36,0:31:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每天所需的食物  求你今天赐给我们\N{\rEng}Give us this day our daily bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.50,0:31:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好像我们饶恕了\N{\rEng}and forgive us our trespasses as we forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.88,0:31:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,得罪我们的人\N{\rEng}those who trespass against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.47,0:31:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让我们陷入试探\N{\rEng}Lead us not into temptation,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.51,0:31:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,救我们脱离那恶者\N{\rEng}but deliver us from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.85,0:31:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔戈今天很愉快\N{\rEng}kilgore had had a pretty good day for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.12,0:31:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们享受牛扒  啤酒\N{\rEng}They choppered in the T-bones and the beer...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.32,0:31:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,将基地变成沙滩派对\N{\rEng}and turned the LZ into a beach party.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.95,0:31:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们越想营造家的感觉\N{\rEng}The more they tried to make it just like home...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.82,0:31:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,便越怀念家\N{\rEng}the more they made everybody miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.43,0:31:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要半生的  不是要冻肉\N{\rEng}Make my meat rare--rare but not cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.74,0:31:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜他不是个差劲的军官\N{\rEng}Well, he wasn't a bad officer, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.24,0:32:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他爱下属  和他在一起有安全感\N{\rEng}He loved his boys, and you felt safe with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.88,0:32:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他有特殊的魅力\N{\rEng}He was one of those guys that had that weird light around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.61,0:32:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但在战场上  他会爱惜身体\N{\rEng}You just knew he wasn't gonna get so much as a scratch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.92,0:32:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的任务怎样了  上尉？\N{\rEng}What happened to your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.85,0:32:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老川把你们都忘了吗？\N{\rEng}Nha Trang forget all about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.26,0:32:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,空降兵\N{\rEng}Airborne.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.07,0:32:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\rEng}Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.73,0:32:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可经两处进入河道\N{\rEng}two places we can get into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.74,0:32:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错  -这两处\N{\rEng}-Yeah.  -Here and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.64,0:32:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然三角洲很宽阔\N{\rEng}It's a pretty wide delta,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.69,0:32:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有这两处我肯定可进入\N{\rEng}but these are the only two spots I'm sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.78,0:32:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你指的这个村庄不敢领教  威尔德\N{\rEng}That village you're pointing at is kind of hairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.95,0:32:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么意思？  -就是说很危险\N{\rEng}-What do you mean ''hairy,'' sir?  -It's hairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.48,0:32:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有重型武器驻守\N{\rEng}Got some pretty heavy ordnance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.18,0:32:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不时在那丢几艘侦察艇\N{\rEng}I lost a few recon ships in there now and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.19,0:32:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那该死的村子叫什么？\N{\rEng}What's the name of that goddamn village?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.82,0:32:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,云东道或云东里\N{\rEng}Vin Drin Dop.  Dop or Lop?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.53,0:32:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,越南鬼起的名字都差不多\N{\rEng}Damn gook names all sound the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.53,0:32:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克  你了解云东道的这里吗？\N{\rEng}Mike, you know anything about this point at Vin Drin Dop?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.03,0:32:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,浪头没得说\N{\rEng}That's a fantastic peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.24,0:33:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-浪头？  -近2米高的浪\N{\rEng}-Peak?  -About six foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.34,0:33:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很少见  左右滑面也很长\N{\rEng}It's an outstanding peak. It's got both the long right and left slide...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.21,0:33:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,浪形前所未见  是冲浪胜地\N{\rEng}with a bowl section that's unbelievable.It's just tube city.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.68,0:33:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不早说？  好浪头\N{\rEng}Why didn't you tell me that before? A good peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.75,0:33:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这鬼地方  没见过好浪头\N{\rEng}There aren't any good peaks in this whole shitty country.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.62,0:33:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-只有碎浪  -但那真的很危险\N{\rEng}-It's all goddamn beach break.  -It's really hairy in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.29,0:33:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克唐纳就死在那\N{\rEng}That's where we lost McDonald.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.82,0:33:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受了重创  那是越共的据点\N{\rEng}They shot the hell out of us there. That's Charlie's point.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.03,0:33:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  我们可在明天黎明出发\N{\rEng}Sir, we can go in there tomorrow at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.73,0:33:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨常有离岸的微风\N{\rEng}There's always a good offshore breeze in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.27,0:33:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,船可能开不进\N{\rEng}We may not be able to get the boat in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.27,0:33:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,河口恐怕吃水太浅\N{\rEng}The draft at the mouth of that river may be too shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.74,0:33:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可吊起船\N{\rEng}We'll pick your boat up
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.19,0:33:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,放在你希望的地方\N{\rEng}and put it down like a baby where you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.84,0:33:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是空中骑兵九团一队\N{\rEng}This is the First of the Ninth, Air-Cav, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.65,0:33:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,空中机动部队\N{\rEng}Air mobile!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.48,0:33:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我能自由选择起降点！\N{\rEng}I can take that point and hold it as long as I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.98,0:33:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去那条河的任何地方  上尉\N{\rEng}You can get anyplace up that river that suits you, young Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.15,0:33:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  近2米的浪头\N{\rEng}Hell, a six-foot peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.09,0:33:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊  开一架武装直升机回总部\N{\rEng}Take a gunship back to the division.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.39,0:34:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  跟迈克一起去  让他挑块冲浪板\N{\rEng}Lance, go with Mike and let him pick out a board for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.63,0:34:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拿来我那8ˊ6的冲浪板\N{\rEng}Bring me my Yater Spoon, the eight-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.33,0:34:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不知道  长官  那  -什么事  大兵？\N{\rEng}-I don't know, sir  -What is it, soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.73,0:34:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那很危险  是越共据点\N{\rEng}It's hairy in there. It's Charlie's point.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.54,0:34:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,越共不冲浪\N{\rEng}Charlie don't surf!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.76,0:34:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,天呀  克林  难以置信！ 看\N{\rEng}Hey,Jesus, Clean, you ain't gonna believe this. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.77,0:34:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要吊起船！\N{\rEng}Hey, man! They're pickin' up the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.77,0:34:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉如何  吉米？\N{\rEng}How are you feeling,Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.31,0:34:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没得说  长官！\N{\rEng}Like a mean motherfucker, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.78,0:34:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  全速前进\N{\rEng}All right, son, let 'er rip.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.25,0:34:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEng}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.57,0:36:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不习惯用轻板\N{\rEng}I never have got used to a light board.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.33,0:36:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,从不习惯\N{\rEng}I can't get used to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.64,0:36:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-我习惯用重板  -没错  它不好用\N{\rEng}-I'm used to a heavy board.  -I know, it's a real drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.51,0:36:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-你用重板还是轻板？  -重板\N{\rEng}-You prefer a heavy or light board?  -Heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.71,0:36:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的？  -真的\N{\rEng}-Really?  -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.18,0:36:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为年轻人爱轻板\N{\rEng}I thought all the young guys like lighter boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.55,0:36:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没法站在板尖冲浪\N{\rEng}You can't ride the nose on those.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.55,0:36:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵6号  公爵6号\N{\rEng}Big Duke Six.Duke Six to Eagle Thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.35,0:36:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是神鹰7号  我们已发现目标\N{\rEng}This is Eagle Thrust Seven. We've got it spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.38,0:36:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,神鹰  向2-7-0方位飞\N{\rEng}Put on heading two-seven-zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.32,0:36:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,保持战斗队形\N{\rEng}Assume attack formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.16,0:36:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  公爵  我们正进入\N{\rEng}That's a roger, Big Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.06,0:36:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来了\N{\rEng}We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.23,0:36:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将迎着旭日低飞\N{\rEng}Hey, Lance, we'll come in low out of the rising sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.70,0:36:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,离目的地约1英里时  会放音乐\N{\rEng}About a mile out, we'll put on the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.43,0:36:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-音乐？  -没错  瓦格纳的《女武神》\N{\rEng}-Music?  -Yeah, I use Wagner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.97,0:36:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,吓怕越共  部下都喜欢\N{\rEng}Scares the hell out of the slopes. My boys love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.24,0:36:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要放音乐了\N{\rEng}Hey, they're gonna play music!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.88,0:37:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么坐在头盔上？\N{\rEng}How come all you guys sit on your helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.65,0:37:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不会炸掉卵蛋\N{\rEng}So we don't get our balls blown off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.23,0:37:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵告诉神鹰  开始心理战\N{\rEng}Big Duke Six to Eagle Thrust. Put on psy war op.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.64,0:37:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,开大声点  是罗密欧狐步舞\N{\rEng}Make it loud. This is a Romeo Fox Trot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.71,0:37:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跳舞吗？\N{\rEng}Shall we dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.58,0:37:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.82,0:40:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-来吧  -好啊\N{\rEng}-Come on!  -All right. Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.07,0:40:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,发现林木线那有几个人\N{\rEng}We got a couple--at that tree line.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.60,0:40:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在猛轰\N{\rEng}We're taking fire from the holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.94,0:40:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,跑啊  越共！\N{\rEng}Run, Charlie!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.38,0:40:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这会让一切都烧起来\N{\rEng}This should make everything burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.26,0:40:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,前面有几个人\N{\rEng}We got a couple of people ahead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.76,0:40:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,下面怎么了？\N{\rEng}What's going down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.06,0:40:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有机关枪  炸了它！\N{\rEng}We got an automatic! Shoot to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.93,0:40:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,炸了它！\N{\rEng}Shoot to kill in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.30,0:40:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,发现下面有重武器\N{\rEng}I spotted a large weapon down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.13,0:40:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去看看\N{\rEng}We're gonna go down and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.14,0:40:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  这是狐步舞  我们要到了\N{\rEng}All right, this is Fox Trot. We're pullin'in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.15,0:41:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,射得好！\N{\rEng}What a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.35,0:41:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没得说  红组\N{\rEng}Outstanding, Red Team. Outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.05,0:41:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,奖一箱啤酒\N{\rEng}Get you a case of beer for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.41,0:41:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,6-4-1-0  我们在村庄上空\N{\rEng}Six-four-one-zero, we're over the village right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.31,0:41:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见院里有辆车  我要去看看\N{\rEng}I see a vehicle in the courtyard. I'm gonna check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.42,0:41:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  飞鹰  做得好\N{\rEng}Well done, Hawks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.38,0:41:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沿林木线扫射\N{\rEng}Want some twenty-Mike-Mike-Vulcan along those tree lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.79,0:41:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,轰掉他们\N{\rEng}Ripple the shit out of'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.79,0:41:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,桥上有辆车  配有50口径机枪\N{\rEng}Got a vehicle on the bridge, 50 caliber on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.16,0:41:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他正过桥  想再次补充弹药\N{\rEng}He's moving across to resupply the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.53,0:41:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵6号  作好掩护  我亲自出马\N{\rEng}Big Duke Six, clear the area. I'm coming down myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.76,0:41:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人从不认输吗？\N{\rEng}Don't these people ever give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.34,0:41:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,射得好  基尔戈！\N{\rEng}Nice shot, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.21,0:42:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-妈的  -没事\N{\rEng}-Shit!  -All right, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.28,0:42:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只是颗照明弹！\N{\rEng}It's just a flare! It's a flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.61,0:42:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-让我出去！  -别这样讲\N{\rEng}-Gotta get outta here!  -Un-ass that shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.75,0:42:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,把它弄出去！\N{\rEng}Get it outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.92,0:42:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,把它弄出去  别紧张  只是颗照明弹\N{\rEng}Get it out. It's just a flare. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.02,0:42:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都好吧？  兰斯  你没事吧？\N{\rEng}Everybody all right? Lance?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.12,0:42:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没事！\N{\rEng}I'm fiIne!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.47,0:42:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下！\N{\rEng}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.66,0:42:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去！ 我不去！\N{\rEng}I'm not going! I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.30,0:42:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去！\N{\rEng}I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.61,0:43:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,第二波进入广场\N{\rEng}We just got a secondary down there in the plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.78,0:43:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝3  蓝4  坚守岗位\N{\rEng}Hold on to your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.48,0:43:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵6号  这里有人受伤\N{\rEng}Duke Six, we've got wounded down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.80,0:43:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抬担架来！\N{\rEng}Get a stretcher over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.57,0:43:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,天呀！ 救我！\N{\rEng}-Please, God! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.47,0:43:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-给他注射吗啡！  -天哪！\N{\rEng}-Give him some morphine.  -My God! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.38,0:43:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,0-3-7-7-4-2\N{\rEng}Seven-four-two!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.98,0:43:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,医疗直升机呢？\N{\rEng}Where's that duster?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.81,0:43:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要伤兵在15分钟内送到医院\N{\rEng}I want my wounded out of there and in the hospital in 1 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.88,0:43:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我的人撤出\N{\rEng}I want my men out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.62,0:43:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,留人掩护公爵号\N{\rEng}Somebody stay in there tight with Big Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.62,0:43:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是10-10  我们准备降落\N{\rEng}This is Ten-Ten. We're gonna be in,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.38,0:43:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,抬他们进来  然后离开\N{\rEng}throw 'em on and get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.25,0:44:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她有手榴弹！\N{\rEng}She's got a grenade!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.51,0:44:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她有手榴弹！\N{\rEng}She's got a grenade!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.28,0:44:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  那东西被炸飞了\N{\rEng}The whole thing blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.99,0:44:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-她引爆了  -他妈的野蛮人\N{\rEng}-She blew the shit  -Fucking savages.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.39,0:44:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,找架救伤直升机\N{\rEng}Get a medevac.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.59,0:44:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  她是个笨蛋  我要打死她\N{\rEng}Holy Christ, she's a SAP.I'm gonna get that dinkbitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.26,0:44:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,去那边  钟尼  射准点\N{\rEng}Get over there, Johnny. Roll that right skid right up her ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.34,0:44:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须炸掉些树\N{\rEng}We gotta get some air in these trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.90,0:44:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真烦和下面的敌人纠缠\N{\rEng}It's goddamn eat-up with enemy down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.67,0:44:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,直升机着火  多处被击中\N{\rEng}I'm taking fire. I'm taking hits all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.74,0:44:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,3点钟方向！ 3点钟方向\N{\rEng}Three o'clock! I'm drawing heavy fiIre!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.38,0:44:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我身陷火中  大火\N{\rEng}I'm hit! Mayday! Mayday!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.51,0:44:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我被击中了！  救命！  尾部旋翼松脱  还能控制\N{\rEng}I'm goin'in.My tail rotor's out. I got control.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.76,0:45:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-觉得怎样？  -惊心动魄\N{\rEng}-What do you think?  -Wow! This is really exciting, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.49,0:45:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是说浪！\N{\rEng}No! No! The waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.36,0:45:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-浪头！  -噢  是的\N{\rEng}-The waves!  -Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.93,0:45:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看  涌向两个方向\N{\rEng}Look at that. Breaks both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.80,0:45:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\rEng}Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.73,0:45:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧！  近2米高的大浪\N{\rEng}Watch.Look! Good six-foot swells!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.49,0:45:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,过来  兰斯\N{\rEng}Come here, Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.26,0:45:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小心！\N{\rEng}Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.57,0:45:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个着陆点仍很危险\N{\rEng}This LZ is still pretty hot, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.10,0:45:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,去别处冲浪吧\N{\rEng}Maybe you ought to surf somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.81,0:45:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂冲浪吗？   少校？\N{\rEng}What do you know about surfiIng, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.64,0:45:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你从他妈的新泽西来\N{\rEng}You're from goddamn New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.25,0:46:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,过来！\N{\rEng}Come here! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.65,0:46:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-换衣服  -现在吗  长官？\N{\rEng}-Change!  -You mean right now, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.22,0:46:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我要试试浪头  换衣服\N{\rEng}I wanna see how rideable that stuff is. Go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.32,0:46:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这里仍很危险\N{\rEng}It's still pretty hairy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.19,0:46:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想冲浪吗  大兵？  -想  长官\N{\rEng}-Do you wanna surf, soldier?  -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.19,0:46:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  不冲浪  便打仗\N{\rEng}That's good, son, 'cause you either surf or fiIght.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.89,0:46:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了？\N{\rEng}That clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.83,0:46:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEng}Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.43,0:46:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我来掩护他们  替兰斯拿块冲浪板\N{\rEng}I'll cover for 'em.And bring a board for Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.67,0:46:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,船不到  什么也没有\N{\rEng}We can't do shit until the boat gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.21,0:46:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  我打赌你一定迫不及待\N{\rEng}Lance, I'll bet you can't wait to get out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.71,0:46:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么？  -看见浪涌向两边了吗？\N{\rEng}-What?  -See how they break both ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.81,0:46:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在同一时间可一人向左  一人向右\N{\rEng}One guy can break right, one left, simultaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.75,0:46:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为如何？\N{\rEng}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.15,0:46:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是等涨潮吧\N{\rEng}We ought to wait for the tide to come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.42,0:46:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-兰斯  过来  看！  -小心！\N{\rEng}-Come here. Look.  -Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.59,0:46:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,6小时后才涨潮！\N{\rEng}The tide doesn't come in for six hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.13,0:46:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你想在这等6小时？\N{\rEng}You wanna wait here for six hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.33,0:46:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,酋长！\N{\rEng}Yo! Chief! Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.98,0:47:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  各位  别躲了\N{\rEng}Okay, fellas, quit hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.18,0:47:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧！ 去冲浪\N{\rEng}Come on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.75,0:47:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,该死！\N{\rEng}Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.35,0:47:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不认为休假来冲浪有点冒险吗！\N{\rEng}Don't you think it's a little risky for R and R?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.95,0:47:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉  我说在这片海滩冲浪安全\N{\rEng}If I say it's safe to surf this beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.75,0:47:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它就安全！\N{\rEng}it's safe to surf this beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.65,0:47:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怕在这冲浪\N{\rEng}I'm not afraid to surf this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.66,0:47:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在这鬼地方冲浪\N{\rEng}I'll surf this fuckin' place.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.53,0:47:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给我通话器  大兵\N{\rEng}Give me that R-T, soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.15,0:47:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,鸽子4号  这是公爵6号  妈的！\N{\rEng}Dove Four, this is Big Duke Six. Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.55,0:47:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你们沿林木线轰炸！\N{\rEng}I want that tree line bombed!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.52,0:47:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵6号  收到  鸽子1至3号  准备\N{\rEng}Big Duke Six, roger. Dove One-Three, stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.42,0:47:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,炸他们个片甲不留！\N{\rEng}Blow them into the Stone Age, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.58,0:47:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-尽快！ 完毕  -不  回去！\N{\rEng}-Out!  -No, back, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.68,0:47:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  让我处理吧\N{\rEng}Let me take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.08,0:47:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,把它拿开！\N{\rEng}Get that out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.33,0:47:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-对不起  -过来  好的\N{\rEng}-I'm sorry.  -Come here now. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.44,0:47:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,退后  不  太太  抱歉！\N{\rEng}No, ma'am. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.34,0:47:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,吉米！\N{\rEng}Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.40,0:47:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,飞鹰1  2号  鸽子1至3号\N{\rEng}Hawk One-Two, Dove One-Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.21,0:47:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要用凝固汽油弹沿林木线轰炸\N{\rEng}They need some napalm in the tree line.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.79,0:47:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能办到吗？\N{\rEng}Can you put it down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.61,0:47:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  1至3号  我们准备投弹\N{\rEng}Right, One-Three. We're fixin' to fuck with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.14,0:47:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,目标？\N{\rEng}What's the target?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.85,0:48:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,遏止林木线附近的迫击炮火\N{\rEng}We're trying to suppress some mortar fire off the tree line down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.00,0:48:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  我们来了\N{\rEng}Roger. Here we come.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.30,0:48:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  全力进攻\N{\rEng}Good. Give it all you got.Bring in all your ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.14,0:48:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的直升机  送他去医院\N{\rEng}Put him in my chopper. Get him back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.61,0:48:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  不  你要和他一道  -快！ 走吧！\N{\rEng}-No, no, no, you got to go with him.  -Come on! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.08,0:48:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧！ 告诉我的人  我要我的冲浪板！\N{\rEng}Get it outta here!Tell my guys I want my board!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.92,0:48:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵6号  战机已上路\N{\rEng}Big Duke Six, this is Dove One-Three.The jets are inbound now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.73,0:48:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有30秒\N{\rEng}You got about 30 seconds to bomb station.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.33,0:48:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,撤回所有人  并做好掩护\N{\rEng}Get your people backand heads down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.14,0:48:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,轰炸会很猛烈\N{\rEng}This is gonna be a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.66,0:48:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\rEng}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.09,0:48:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方很快会清理好  别担心\N{\rEng}We'll have this place cleaned up in a jiffy, son. Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.40,0:48:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,给我短裤\N{\rEng}Give me those shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.09,0:48:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是空中骑兵的  我们送给你当礼物\N{\rEng}These are from the Air-Cav, a present from me and the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.92,0:48:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看你穿上它冲浪  行吗？\N{\rEng}I want to see you do your stuff in 'em out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.83,0:49:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你闻到了吗？\N{\rEng}You smell that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.97,0:49:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-你闻到了吗？  -什么？\N{\rEng}-Do you smell that?  -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.49,0:49:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,凝固汽油弹\N{\rEng}Napalm, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.96,0:49:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,气味独一无二\N{\rEng}Nothing else in the world smells like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.56,0:49:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  前进！\N{\rEng}Come on. Move it! Move it! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.80,0:49:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢凝固汽油弹  在清晨的味道\N{\rEng}I love the smell of napalm in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.73,0:49:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次  我们连续12小时炸一座山头\N{\rEng}You know, one time we had a hill bombed for 1 2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.80,0:49:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,炸完后  我爬上山\N{\rEng}When it was all over, I walked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.97,0:49:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一具越共的腐臭尸体  也没发现\N{\rEng}We didn't fiInd one of them, not one stinking dink body.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.24,0:49:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但那汽油味\N{\rEng}But the smell--You know, that gasoline smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.48,0:49:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,整座山都飘散着\N{\rEng}The whole hill smelled like...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.59,0:49:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利的气味\N{\rEng}victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.18,0:49:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这仗终有一天会结束\N{\rEng}Someday this war's gonna end.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.25,0:50:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  有风！\N{\rEng}Lance! The wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.91,0:50:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-有风！ -什么？\N{\rEng}-The wind!  -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.12,0:50:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,它在吹向岸边！\N{\rEng}It's blowin' onshore!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.25,0:50:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,吹向这里来\N{\rEng}It's gonna blow this place out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.99,0:50:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-会破坏浪  -不爽！\N{\rEng}-It's gonna ruin it!  -Not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.26,0:50:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-它要吹散浪头！  -是该死的凝固汽油弹\N{\rEng}-It's gonna blow out!  -It's the goddamn napalm!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.59,0:50:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-就是它引起的  -我知道\N{\rEng}-That's what's doin' it! -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.46,0:50:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真对不起  上校  恐怕你说得对\N{\rEng}I'm really sorry, Colonel. I'm afraid that does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.21,0:50:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他名气大\N{\rEng}The kid's got a reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.71,0:50:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别指望他在泥水里冲浪\N{\rEng}You can't expect him to surf those sloppy waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.05,0:50:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-我懂  -我是个艺术家  基尔戈\N{\rEng}-I understand.  -I'm an artist, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.62,0:50:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不能在泥水里冲浪\N{\rEng}I couldn't surf that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.59,0:50:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  兰斯  我道歉  但不是我的错\N{\rEng}I apologize. It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.72,0:50:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,海浪被凝固汽油弹吹散\N{\rEng}The waves are gettin' blown out by the napalm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.59,0:50:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别怪我\N{\rEng}Don't get me wrong--
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.76,0:50:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸的气浪引起了漩涡\N{\rEng}It was the bombs causing a vortex with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.60,0:50:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受你的道歉\N{\rEng}I accept your apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.66,0:50:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能再等20分钟\N{\rEng}But if you could hang around 20 minutes--
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.43,0:50:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-下次吧  基尔戈  -就20分钟\N{\rEng}-Some other time, Bill. -Just 20 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.64,0:50:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是个艺术家  -别停！\N{\rEng}-I'm an artist.  -keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.64,0:50:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  试试\N{\rEng}Okay, give it a try, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.54,0:50:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一人向左  一人向右\N{\rEng}One goes left and one goes right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.54,0:50:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看  兰斯\N{\rEng}Look, Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.28,0:51:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想冲浪吗？  -是的！\N{\rEng}-You through surfiIng?  -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.81,0:51:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-想对上校说再见吗？  -不\N{\rEng}-Wanna say good-bye to the colonel?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.82,0:51:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-你肯定？  -肯定！\N{\rEng}-You sure?  -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.38,0:51:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-快他妈离开  -只是该死的凝固汽油弹！\N{\rEng}-Get the fuck outta here.  -It's the napalm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.65,0:51:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就等20分钟！\N{\rEng}Just wait 20 minutes!
