Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.18,0:51:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一直在找你\N{\rEng}They've been lookin' for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.75,0:51:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-别丢下我  -你到底要去哪？\N{\rEng}-Don't leave without me!  -Where the fuck you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.99,0:51:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小心！\N{\rEng}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.16,0:51:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那是上校的冲浪板！\N{\rEng}That's the colonel's surfboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.83,0:51:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,离远点  它是我的\N{\rEng}Incoming!Hey, get the fuck off me! It's mine!
