Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.60,0:52:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这仗终有一天会结束\N{\rEng}Someday this war's gonna end.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.00,0:52:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对船上的小子们是好事\N{\rEng}That would bejust fine with the boys on the boat.
