Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.02,0:52:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好正点！\N{\rEng}Buddha time. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.52,0:52:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊  真不错  混蛋\N{\rEng}All right, that's great, you motherfuckers. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.95,0:52:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,若基尔戈这样打仗\N{\rEng}If that's how kilgore fought the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.52,0:52:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始奇怪他们究竟  和库尔兹有什么不同\N{\rEng}I began to wonder what they really had against kurtz.
