Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.40,0:55:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\rEng}Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.37,0:55:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢深入虎穴吧  上尉？\N{\rEng}You like it like that, Captain, when it's hot, hairy?
