Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.95,0:56:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没机会知道\N{\rEng}Maybe you'll get a chance to know
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.68,0:56:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你在俄亥俄的工厂里是干嘛的\N{\rEng}what the fuck you are in some factory in Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.92,0:56:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,酋长  我想上岸摘芒果  行吗？\N{\rEng}Hey, Chief, I'm gonna go get those mangos now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.74,0:56:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-找个人陪你  -我会带着他\N{\rEng}-Take somebody with ya.  -Yeah, I'll take--
