Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.09,0:56:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨？\N{\rEng}Chef?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.16,0:56:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  长官？  -他们为什么这样叫你？\N{\rEng}-Yes, sir?  -How come they call you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.89,0:56:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-叫我什么  长官？  -大厨\N{\rEng}-Call me what, sir?  -Chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.76,0:56:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你喜欢芒果之类的吗？\N{\rEng}Because you like mangos and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.70,0:56:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不  长官  我真是大厨\N{\rEng}No, sir, I'm a real chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.37,0:56:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是个  酱汁师    -酱汁师？\N{\rEng}-I'm a saucier.  -Saucier?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.24,0:56:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir. See,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.27,0:56:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  我来自新奥尔良\N{\rEng}I come from New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.21,0:56:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,自小就被培养  要做个伟大的酱汁师\N{\rEng}I was raised to be a saucier, a great saucier.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.81,0:56:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么是酱汁师？  -我们专攻酱汁\N{\rEng}-What's a saucier?  -You specialize in sauces.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.09,0:56:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,附近一定有芒果树\N{\rEng}Gotta be a mango tree here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.29,0:57:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来应去巴黎\N{\rEng}Then, I was supposed to go to Paris...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.16,0:57:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,入读厨艺学校\N{\rEng}study at the EscoffiIer school.
