Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.00,0:57:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,听说吃得较好\N{\rEng}Heard they had better food.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.70,0:57:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还有厨子学校\N{\rEng}Cook school--that did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.14,0:57:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么样？  -你不想听的\N{\rEng}-Yeah, how's that?  -You don't wanna hear about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.74,0:57:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,近百米的上等肉排列在面前\N{\rEng}They lined us up in front of a hundred yards of prime rib.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.01,0:57:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人列队看着\N{\rEng}All of us, you know, lined up lookin' at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.35,0:57:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,肉质极佳  切割很好\N{\rEng}MagnifiIcent meat. Really! Beautifully marbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.22,0:57:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,接着  他们把肉扔进大锅\N{\rEng}Next thing, they're throwing the meat into these big cauldrons--
