Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.33,0:57:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我看着肉色变灰\N{\rEng}I looked inside, man. It was turning gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.47,0:58:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈不敢相信\N{\rEng}I couldn't fucking believe that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.10,0:58:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我申请入无线电技师学校\N{\rEng}That's when I applied for radioman school,
