Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.48,0:58:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\rEng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.67,0:58:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,越共？\N{\rEng}Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.12,0:59:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是老虎！  狗娘养的！\N{\rEng}It's a tiger!Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.73,0:59:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老虎！ 是老虎！\N{\rEng}It's a tiger, man! It's a tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.06,0:59:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位  兰斯  准备\N{\rEng}Battle stations. Lance, up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.46,0:59:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-M60机枪戒备  克林  -收到\N{\rEng}-Get on your 60!  -Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.43,0:59:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,天呀！ 大厨  快走！\N{\rEng}Holy shit! Chef, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.90,0:59:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的老虎！\N{\rEng}A fuckin' tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.00,0:59:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉  快来！\N{\rEng}Captain, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.30,0:59:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快走！\N{\rEng}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.74,0:59:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,队长  你说得对！ 永不要下船\N{\rEng}You were right. Never get out of the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.67,0:59:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,克林  开动M60机枪？\N{\rEng}Bring that 60 forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.77,0:59:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,永不要下船！ 我要记住！\N{\rEng}I gotta remember! Never get out of the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.64,0:59:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,永不要下船！\N{\rEng}Never get out of the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.72,0:59:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了？  有多少人？\N{\rEng}What happen? How many is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.45,0:59:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-他妈的老虎！  -老虎？\N{\rEng}-A fuckin' tiger!  -What? A tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.59,0:59:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了！\N{\rEng}Yes! I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.39,0:59:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是无胆鬼\N{\rEng}I've had the whole goddamn fuckin' shit, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.09,0:59:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回家\N{\rEng}You can kiss my ass on the county square...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.67,0:59:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想留下来\N{\rEng}because I'm fuckin' buggin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.60,1:00:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入海军  不是为了送死\N{\rEng}I don't fuckin' need it! I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.91,1:00:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想做厨师\N{\rEng}All I wanted to do was fuckin' cook!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.28,1:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想学烹饪\N{\rEng}I just wanted to learn to fuckin' cook, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.51,1:00:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\rEng}You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.85,1:00:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了  没事了\N{\rEng}You're all right. You're gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.19,1:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要下船  永不下船\N{\rEng}Never get out of the fuckin' boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.43,1:00:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  老虎！\N{\rEng}Hi, tiger! Bye, tiger! Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.67,1:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,永不下船\N{\rEng}Never get out of the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.20,1:00:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是至理名言\N{\rEng}Absolutely, goddamn right...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.91,1:00:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你不打算回头\N{\rEng}unless you were going all the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.51,1:00:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,古华特下了船\N{\rEng}kurtz got off the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.08,1:00:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他离经叛道\N{\rEng}He split from the whole fuckin'program.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.72,1:00:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样？\N{\rEng}How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.49,1:00:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他第一次来时  遇见什么？\N{\rEng}What did he see here that first tour?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.80,1:01:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那时他已38岁\N{\rEng}Thirty-eight fucking years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.41,1:01:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,若加入特种部队\N{\rEng}If you joined the Green Berets...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.01,1:01:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,晋升至上校已是极限\N{\rEng}there was no way you'd ever get above colonel.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.58,1:01:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,古华特知道他要放弃什么\N{\rEng}kurtz knew what he was giving up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.62,1:01:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我对他认识越多\N{\rEng}The more I read and began to understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.58,1:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,越发敬佩他\N{\rEng}the more I admired him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.29,1:01:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他的家人  朋友  也不了解他\N{\rEng}His family and friends couldn't understand it...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.79,1:01:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们无法说服他\N{\rEng}and they couldn't talk him out of it.
