Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.50,1:01:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当他以辞职要胁  他们屈服了\N{\rEng}But when he threatened to resign, they gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.70,1:01:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,班上的后生仔  比他年轻一半\N{\rEng}The next youngest guy in his class was half his age.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.34,1:01:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必定认为这老人家\N{\rEng}They must have thought he was some far-out old man...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.58,1:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,无法完成课程\N{\rEng}humping it over that course.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.51,1:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我16岁入读  几乎要了我的命\N{\rEng}I did it when I was 1 6. It damn near wasted me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.75,1:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他真有种\N{\rEng}A tough motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.36,1:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了课程\N{\rEng}He finished it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.46,1:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能晋升将军\N{\rEng}He could have gone for general...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.97,1:02:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但选择了自己道路\N{\rEng}but he went for himself instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.37,1:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的伊娃：今天很特别\N{\rEng}Dear Eva...Today was really a new one.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.28,1:02:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,差点被老虎生吞\N{\rEng}Almost got eaten alive by a fuckin' tiger.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.05,1:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真的难以想像\N{\rEng}Really un-fucking believable, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.52,1:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要带伟利上尉  逆流而上\N{\rEng}We're taking this guy, Captain Willard, up the river...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.32,1:02:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不肯讲出目的地\N{\rEng}but he hasn't told us yet where we're taking him.
