Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.96,1:13:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真该给这家伙一枚银星勋章\N{\rEng}Should have given the fucker a Silver Star.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.80,1:13:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,越南人都是无赖  对吧？\N{\rEng}Bummer for the gook though, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.14,1:14:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,早安  越南\N{\rEng}Good morning, Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.31,1:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是陆军广播员赞克约翰逊\N{\rEng}I'm Army Specialist ZackJohnson on AMVN.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.96,1:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,西贡市区现在约28度\N{\rEng}It's about 82 degrees in downtown Saigon right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.73,1:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,非常潮湿\N{\rEng}also very humid.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.70,1:14:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,西贡市长有重要消息给所有\N{\rEng}We have an important message for all GI's...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.90,1:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,驻扎的美国士兵\N{\rEng}who are living off base from the mayor of Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.41,1:14:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他希望你们把衣物挂在室内\N{\rEng}He'd like you to hang your laundry up indoors
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.02,1:14:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是晾在窗台上\N{\rEng}instead of on the windowsills.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.84,1:14:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,市长希望西贡保持美观\N{\rEng}The mayor wants you to keep Saigon beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.15,1:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  播放一首经典老歌\N{\rEng}Now here's another blast from the past going out
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.80,1:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,给大山姆  他正独自和\N{\rEng}to Big Sam who's all alone out there
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.70,1:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,第35步兵团第一营一起  在安溪的火力小队\N{\rEng}with the 1 st Battalion, 35th Infantry...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.17,1:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也要献给他们英俊的指挥官\N{\rEng}and dedicated by the fire team to their groovy CO.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.91,1:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-滚石乐队的《（我无法得到）满足》  -好啊！\N{\rEng}-The Rolling Stones, ''Satisfaction. '' -All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.41,1:14:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当心  克林！\N{\rEng}Watch out, Clean!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.01,1:14:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,下来！\N{\rEng}Get down, bubba!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.41,1:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住  兰斯！\N{\rEng}Hang on, Lance!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.12,1:15:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,下来！\N{\rEng}Get down, bubba!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.12,1:15:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们你做到了  兰斯\N{\rEng}Tell 'em you did it, Lance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.31,1:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊！\N{\rEng}All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.58,1:15:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,当心  兰斯！\N{\rEng}Look out, Lance!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.17,1:15:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,《献身与平叛》\N{\rEng}Commitment and Counterinsurgency...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.94,1:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特E.库尔兹上校著\N{\rEng}by cononel Walt E.kurtz
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.51,1:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们的军官和队伍\N{\rEng}As long as our officers and troops perform...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.28,1:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都是来逛一年的\N{\rEng}tours of duty limited to one year...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.68,1:15:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会一直是外行\N{\rEng}they will remain dilettantes in war and tourists in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.71,1:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只要冰啤酒  热菜  摇滚乐\N{\rEng}As long as cold beer, hot food, rockand roll...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.58,1:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,和其他一切开心事照旧\N{\rEng}and all the other amenities remain the expected norm...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.58,1:16:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的指挥就只会虚弱无力\N{\rEng}our conduct of the war will gain only impotence.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.12,1:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要精锐部队\N{\rEng}We need fewer men, and better.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.68,1:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们肯献身\N{\rEng}If they were committed, this war could be won...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.99,1:16:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,用现有军队的  四分之一也可取胜\N{\rEng}with a fourth of our present force. ''
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.99,1:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的  害怕了\N{\rEng}Shit. Chicken time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.31,1:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别胡说  兄弟  那该死的\N{\rEng}You ain't shittin', bro. They're motherfuckin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.98,1:16:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是谁？  -怎么了？\N{\rEng}-Who is that?  －What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.65,1:16:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗  拉扎洛？\N{\rEng}Is that you, Lazzaro?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.29,1:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,帐顶着火了！\N{\rEng}Fire on the canopy!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.82,1:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道！ 我知道！ 让开！\N{\rEng}I got it! Get outta there!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.19,1:16:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道！ 我知道！\N{\rEng}Yeah! I got it! I got it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.71,1:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  下去！\N{\rEng}Lance, get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.15,1:16:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,把那东西拿出来！\N{\rEng}Put that fucker out, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.56,1:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到底以为自己在干什么？\N{\rEng}What the fuck they think they're doin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.49,1:17:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,1968年夏末秋初\N{\rEng}Late summer, autumn 1 668.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.77,1:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,库尔兹在高地的巡逻队\N{\rEng}kurtz's patrols in the highlands
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.74,1:17:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,频繁遭伏击\N{\rEng}coming under frequent ambush.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.94,1:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,营地开始瓦解\N{\rEng}The camp started falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.88,1:17:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,11月\N{\rEng}November.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.58,1:17:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,库尔兹命令\N{\rEng}kurtz orders assassination of
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.06,1:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,暗杀越南的3男1女\N{\rEng}three Vietnamese men and one woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.72,1:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,其中两个男的是南越军上校\N{\rEng}Two of the men were colonels in the South Vietnamese army.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.89,1:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军在他老防区的活动逐渐停止\N{\rEng}Enemy activity in his old sector dropped off to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.46,1:18:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,估计这四人他杀对了\N{\rEng}Guess he must have hit the right four people.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.50,1:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他加入了特种部队\N{\rEng}Hejoined the Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.14,1:18:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,之后  他的\N{\rEng}After that his--
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.18,1:18:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,军方尽了最后的努力  想他重回正轨\N{\rEng}The army tried one last time to bring him backinto the fold.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.58,1:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,方法\N{\rEng}methods
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.75,1:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,若他改过  一切既往不咎\N{\rEng}If he'd pulled over it all would have been forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.75,1:18:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,反常\N{\rEng}unsound.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.62,1:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但他一意孤行\N{\rEng}But he kept going.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.55,1:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在进了柬埔寨\N{\rEng}Now he's crossed into Cambodia
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.02,1:18:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不断赢得胜利\N{\rEng}He kept winning it his way.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.69,1:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,和他的这支越南山民军一道\N{\rEng}with this Montagnard army of his
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.42,1:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这时  上级要我出马\N{\rEng}And they called me in.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.73,1:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们奉他若神明\N{\rEng}Man like a god and follow every order,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.14,1:18:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,连极荒谬的命令也执行\N{\rEng}however ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.77,1:18:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,军方失去了他\N{\rEng}They lost him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.84,1:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他消失了\N{\rEng}He was gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.61,1:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只有谣言或零星情报传出\N{\rEng}Nothing but rumors and random intelligence...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.44,1:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,主要来自被俘的越共\N{\rEng}mostly from captured VC.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.41,1:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,越共都知他大名  全惧怕他\N{\rEng}The VC knew his name by now, and they were scared of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.75,1:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他带领部下打游击战\N{\rEng}He and his men were playing hit-and-run
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.78,1:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,并转战到柬埔寨\N{\rEng}all the way into Cambodia.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.26,1:19:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我要去哪\N{\rEng}I know what I'm doin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.40,1:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去白宫\N{\rEng}I'm goin' to the White House to have dinner...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.03,1:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,和总统共进午餐  宝贝\N{\rEng}with the president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.33,1:19:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要去那\N{\rEng}That's where I'm goin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.57,1:19:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨  盖上盖\N{\rEng}Hey, Chef, put the cover on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.61,1:19:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,克林\N{\rEng}Clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.75,1:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他在船上多久了？\N{\rEng}How long has that kid been on this boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.38,1:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,7个月\N{\rEng}Seven months.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.68,1:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是会惹我生气\N{\rEng}He's really specializing in busting my balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.12,1:19:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能  上尉  他也有同感\N{\rEng}Very possible, Captain, he thinks the same of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.02,1:19:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？  你有何高见  酋长？\N{\rEng}Oh, yeah? What do you think, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.83,1:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想法\N{\rEng}I don't think.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.56,1:19:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,上级不让我知道\N{\rEng}My orders say I'm not supposed to know
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.40,1:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要开船去哪  所以我没想法\N{\rEng}where I'm taking this boat so I don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.97,1:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但一见你  不管是哪\N{\rEng}But one look at you, and I know it's gonna be hot,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.00,1:19:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就知会有危险\N{\rEng}wherever it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.15,1:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去上游\N{\rEng}We're going upriver
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.05,1:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,距都朗桥约75公里\N{\rEng}about 7 5 clicks above the Do Lung Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.32,1:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是柬埔寨  上尉\N{\rEng}That's Cambodia, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.81,1:20:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是机密任务\N{\rEng}That's classifiIed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.36,1:20:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不该进柬埔寨\N{\rEng}We're not supposed to be in Cambodia,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.16,1:20:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但那就是我要去的地方\N{\rEng}but that's where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.87,1:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你只管靠近我的目的地\N{\rEng}You just get me close to my destination
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.91,1:20:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你和船员们便可离开\N{\rEng}and I'll cut you and the crew loose.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.69,1:20:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  上尉\N{\rEng}All right, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.08,1:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的儿子\N{\rEng}''Dear Son...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.25,1:20:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你母亲在过去的几星期\N{\rEng}I'm afraid that both you and your mother
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.51,1:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没我的消息\N{\rEng}will have been worried...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.08,1:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕担心坏了\N{\rEng}at not hearing from me during the past weeks...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.05,1:20:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的处境变得艰难了\N{\rEng}but my situation here has become a difficult one.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.99,1:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我正式被军方控以谋杀\N{\rEng}I have been officially accused of murder by the army.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.17,1:21:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的受害人\N{\rEng}The alleged victims
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.78,1:21:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是4名越南双面间谍\N{\rEng}were four Vietnamese double agents.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.60,1:21:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们花了数月搜集证据\N{\rEng}We spent months uncovering them
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.57,1:21:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好揭穿他们\N{\rEng}and accumulating evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.41,1:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,当铁证如山时  我们便行动了\N{\rEng}When absolute proof was completed, we acted--
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.88,1:21:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,像军人一样果敢\N{\rEng}we acted like soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.91,1:21:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,指控是不公正的\N{\rEng}The charges are unjustified.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.45,1:21:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上  他们在这种混乱局面下\N{\rEng}They are, in fact, and in the circumstances of this conflict...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.32,1:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,已完全失去理智\N{\rEng}quite completely insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.00,1:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在战争中\N{\rEng}In a war,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.25,1:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,许多时刻要宽容怜悯\N{\rEng}there are many moments for compassion and tender action.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.77,1:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还有许多时刻要冷酷无情\N{\rEng}There are many moments for ruthless action--
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.64,1:21:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,通常所谓的  冷酷无情\N{\rEng}what is often called ruthless...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.26,1:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在许多情况下  或许只是头脑清晰\N{\rEng}but may in many circumstances be only clarity--
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.76,1:22:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看清了要做什么  并果断行动\N{\rEng}seeing clearly what there is to be done and doing it--''
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.27,1:22:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-派救伤直升机来  完毕  -直接\N{\rEng}-Medevac, come in.  -''directly--
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.47,1:22:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,迅速  清醒\N{\rEng}quickly, awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.35,1:22:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔法  探戈  探戈\N{\rEng}Alpha, Tango, Tango,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.44,1:22:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-回话  探戈  阿尔法  -看哪\N{\rEng}-Echo, Tango, Alpha.  -Looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.44,1:22:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请求救伤直升机  有3  4个人阵亡了  完毕\N{\rEng}Request dust-off.Three, maybe four kIA 's. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.51,1:22:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对这封信\N{\rEng}I trust you
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.19,1:22:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你能有选择的告诉你母亲\N{\rEng}tell your mother what you choose about this letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.10,1:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,至于对我的指控  我不在乎\N{\rEng}As for the charges against me, I am unconcerned.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.50,1:22:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,派救伤直升机来\N{\rEng}Medevac, come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.80,1:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不起他们懦弱  虚伪的道德观\N{\rEng}I am beyond their timid, lying morality,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.00,1:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以心中再无牵挂\N{\rEng}and so I am beyond caring.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.51,1:22:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,救伤直升机  收到了吗？  完毕\N{\rEng}Medevac, do you read?  Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.07,1:22:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全信任你\N{\rEng}You have all my faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.51,1:22:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你的父亲\N{\rEng}Your loving father.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.90,1:22:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪！\N{\rEng}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.17,1:22:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪我和他们无线电联络不上\N{\rEng}No wonder I couldn't get 'em on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.00,1:22:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好一片废墟！\N{\rEng}What a dump.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.07,1:22:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好！ -你怎样？\N{\rEng}-Hi there!  -How ya doin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.91,1:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小船不错\N{\rEng}That's a nice little boat you got there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.15,1:23:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以前从没船来\N{\rEng}Never seen one up here before.
