Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.72,1:51:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你决定加入海军\N{\rEng}I'm so glad you decided to join the navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.06,1:51:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,伊娃不确定  能否和我继续交往\N{\rEng}Eva's not sure she can have a relationship with me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.73,1:51:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我在他妈的2万公里外\N{\rEng}Here I am, 1 3,000 fucking miles away...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.57,1:51:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尽力想维系一段感情\N{\rEng}trying to keep a relationship with my ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.67,1:51:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这比我能对你的朋友  说的多多了\N{\rEng}That's much more than I can say for some of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.61,1:51:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喜欢这带子  我会让爸和家人\N{\rEng}If this tape is any good...I will have Dad and the family
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.08,1:51:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-寄一盘他们自己的  -嗨  兰斯\N{\rEng}-send you a tape of their own. -Hey,Lance.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.10,1:52:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那边！ 在那边！\N{\rEng}There! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.61,1:52:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那边！ 在那边！\N{\rEng}There. Over there!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.06,1:52:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨！ 看看克林！\N{\rEng}Chef, check out Clean!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.06,1:52:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉  克林中枪了\N{\rEng}Captain, he's hit. Clean's hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.50,1:52:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-兰斯！ -小狗跑去哪了？\N{\rEng}-Lance!   -Where'd the dog go?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.67,1:52:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  看看克林\N{\rEng}Lance! They got Clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.64,1:52:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小狗呢？ 我们要回头找小狗\N{\rEng}Where's the dog? We gotta go back and get the dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.77,1:52:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  克林！\N{\rEng}Hey, Clean. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.74,1:52:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能死  混蛋！\N{\rEng}Bubba, you can't die, you fucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.98,1:53:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望很快\N{\rEng}And so I'm hoping that--pretty soon--
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.35,1:53:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  但不要太快\N{\rEng}not too soon--but pretty soon
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.06,1:53:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,会有许多孙子让我宠爱\N{\rEng}I'll have a lot of grandchildren to love and spoil.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.79,1:53:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,当你老婆带他们回来时\N{\rEng}And then when your wife get 'em back,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.82,1:53:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她会欣喜若狂的\N{\rEng}she'll be mad with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.23,1:53:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,连杰茜姨和妈妈\N{\rEng}Even Aunt Jessie and Mama...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.87,1:53:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也会来庆祝你的归家\N{\rEng}will come to celebrate your coming home.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.17,1:53:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶和爸\N{\rEng}Granny and Dad are trying
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.89,1:53:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,正设法存够钱给你买辆车\N{\rEng}to get enough money to get you a car...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.87,1:53:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但别告诉他们\N{\rEng}but don't tell 'em
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.68,1:53:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是我们之间的秘密\N{\rEng}because that's our secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.71,1:53:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何  做正确的事\N{\rEng}Anyhow, do the right thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.65,1:53:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,避开子弹\N{\rEng}stay out of the way of the bullets...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.05,1:53:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,完整无缺的回家\N{\rEng}and bring your heinie home all in one piece...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.16,1:53:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们都很爱你\N{\rEng}because we love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.56,1:53:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你的妈妈\N{\rEng}Love, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.83,1:54:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,克林\N{\rEng}Clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.14,1:55:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\rEng}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.14,1:55:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把望远镜扔给我\N{\rEng}Throw me the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.39,1:55:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  在船头架支16口径\N{\rEng}Lance, take a 1 6 on the bow.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.73,1:55:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨  上60口径\N{\rEng}Chef. Chef. On the 60.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.55,1:56:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.71,1:56:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯\N{\rEng}Lance.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.64,1:57:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护上尉\N{\rEng}Cover the captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.67,1:57:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  掩护上尉\N{\rEng}Cover the captain. Lance.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.63,1:57:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是法国人\N{\rEng}They're French. They're French.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.73,1:57:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨  收起武器！ 收起武器！\N{\rEng}Pick up that weapon! Pick it up! Pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.10,1:57:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别后退  上尉\N{\rEng}Stand fast. Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.34,1:58:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  大家放下武器\N{\rEng}All right, you men. Put down your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.65,1:59:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们死了个人\N{\rEng}We lost one of our men.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.00,1:59:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,法国人一向  对盟友的死致以敬意\N{\rEng}We French always pay respect to the dead of our allies.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.04,1:59:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你们\N{\rEng}You're all welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.51,1:59:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫赫伯特德马海\N{\rEng}My name is Hubert DeMarais.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.12,1:59:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我家的种植园\N{\rEng}This is my family's plantation.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.35,1:59:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有70年了\N{\rEng}It has been such for 70 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.46,1:59:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它会一直这样  除非我们都死了\N{\rEng}And it will be such until we are all dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.27,2:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉  请代表一个心怀感激的国家\N{\rEng}Captain, accept the flag of Tyrone Miller...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.85,2:02:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,接受蒂龙米勒的旗帜\N{\rEng}on behalf of a grateful nation.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.92,2:02:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,食物很美味\N{\rEng}This food is really wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.53,2:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好酒  好酱汁\N{\rEng}The wine, the sauces.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.22,2:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\rEng}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.92,2:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我能跟厨师谈谈吗？\N{\rEng}Hey, can I speak with the chef?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.89,2:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,厨师只讲越南语\N{\rEng}The chef speak only Vietnamese.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.26,2:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别逗了厨艺这么好\N{\rEng}No kidding? He cooks like this
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.14,2:02:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然不会讲法语？\N{\rEng}and he can't even speak French?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.23,2:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  厨师是个越南人\N{\rEng}Hey, Lance, the chef's a slope.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.17,2:02:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯\N{\rEng}Lance.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.45,2:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,波德莱尔的诗\N{\rEng}This is Baudelaire.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:21.35,2:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对孩子来说太残酷\N{\rEng}It's a very cruel poem for children.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.47,2:03:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们需要\N{\rEng}But they need it,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.84,2:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为生活有时很残酷\N{\rEng}'cause life sometimes is very cruel.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.64,2:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见\N{\rEng}As you can see.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.88,2:03:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,靠家人抵抗攻击\N{\rEng}Attack repels by the family.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.08,2:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只为了这场战争\N{\rEng}Just for this war.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.25,2:03:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,越共  58个\N{\rEng}Vietcong, 58.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.94,2:03:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,北越人  12个\N{\rEng}North Vietnamese, 1 2.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.47,2:03:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,南越人  11个\N{\rEng}South Vietnamese, 1 1 .
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.38,2:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,美国人  6个？\N{\rEng}Americans, six?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.65,2:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  可能有误\N{\rEng}Yes. Well, there were perhaps mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.44,2:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,荣幸介绍威尔德上尉\N{\rEng}May I present Captain Willard.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.17,2:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,伞兵团的\N{\rEng}He is of a paratroop regiment.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.12,2:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-萨嫮勒夫人  -上尉\N{\rEng}-Madame Sarrault.  -Captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.44,2:04:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  上尉  只是个有关\N{\rEng}Oh, I'm sorry, Captain. It was just a little story...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.97,2:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,战争期间  巴黎和挨饿的人的小故事\N{\rEng}about Paris and people starving during the war.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.31,2:04:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们围坐在桌旁\N{\rEng}They are all around the table,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.68,2:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,片刻沉默后  一个人说\N{\rEng}and there was a silence and somebody say...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:54.36,2:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有天使经过\N{\rEng}An angel is passing by.''
Dialogue: 0,2:04:56.25,2:04:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,于是另一个人说  我们吃了她\N{\rEng}So somebody said, ''Let's eat it.''
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.16,2:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你们大概要留多久？\N{\rEng}How long can you possibly stay here?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.76,2:05:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\N{\rEng}We stay forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.53,2:05:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是说\N{\rEng}No, no. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.63,2:05:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么不回法国的家？\N{\rEng}why don't you go back home to France?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.37,2:05:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,回家？\N{\rEng}Back home?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.00,2:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的家  上尉\N{\rEng}I mean, this is our home, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.21,2:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-迟早  你们会  -不会\N{\rEng}－Sooner or later, you're--  －No.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.04,2:05:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂我们的心理\N{\rEng}You don't understand our mentality--
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.38,2:05:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,法国军官的心理\N{\rEng}the French offiIcer mentality!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:32.75,2:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  我们输了二战\N{\rEng}At fiIrst, we lose in Second World War.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.18,2:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说你们美国胜了  但法国输了\N{\rEng}I don't say that you Americans win, but we lose.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.05,2:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  爸爸\N{\rEng}Oh, Papa--
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.52,2:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在奠边府  我们败了  在阿尔及利压  我们败了\N{\rEng}In Dien Bien Phu, we lose. In Algeria, we lose.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.39,2:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在印度支那  我们败了！\N{\rEng}In Indochina, we lose!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.76,2:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这里  我们没败！\N{\rEng}But here we don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.95,2:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们坚守着这片土地\N{\rEng}This piece of earth, we keep it.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.05,2:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不会失去它  永远！\N{\rEng}We will never lose it. Never!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.23,2:06:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们美国人\N{\rEng}You Americans.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.66,2:06:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在1945年\N{\rEng}In 1 945, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.48,2:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对日作战后\N{\rEng}after the Japanese war,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.39,2:06:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的总统罗斯福\N{\rEng}your President Roosevelt
Dialogue: 0,2:06:12.88,2:06:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不想让法国人留在印度支那\N{\rEng}didn't want the French people to stay in Indochina.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.99,2:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们美国人  安插进越盟（追随胡志明）\N{\rEng}So...you Americans implant the Vietminh.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.93,2:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-他什么意思？  -这是真的\N{\rEng}-What's he mean?  -Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.92,2:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,越共由美国人创建\N{\rEng}The Vietcong were invented by the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.72,2:06:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,美国人？\N{\rEng}The Americans?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.32,2:06:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  你们取代了法国\N{\rEng}And now you take the French place...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:34.06,2:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,于是  越盟打你们\N{\rEng}and the Vietminh fiIght you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.36,2:06:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能怎样？\N{\rEng}And what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.33,2:06:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,束手无策\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.60,2:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,完全束手无策\N{\rEng}Absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:41.10,2:06:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,越南人很聪明\N{\rEng}The Vietnamese are very intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.68,2:06:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你从不知道他们的想法\N{\rEng}You never know what they think.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.47,2:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们找苏联人帮忙\N{\rEng}The Russian ones who help them,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.28,2:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,说来给我们钱\N{\rEng}Come and give us their money.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.34,2:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是共产党  找中国人说\N{\rEng}We are all Communists. Chinese,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:50.19,2:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们武器  我们都是兄弟\N{\rEng}give us guns. We are all brothers.''
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.21,2:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们讨厌中国人！\N{\rEng}They hate the Chinese!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.55,2:06:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,比起苏联人和中国人\N{\rEng}Maybe they hate the American
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.52,2:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也许还不那么讨厌美国人\N{\rEng}less than the Russian and the Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.95,2:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说  如果明天越南人成了共产党\N{\rEng}I mean, if tomorrow the Vietnamese are Communists...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.15,2:07:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也会是  越南  共产党\N{\rEng}they will be Vietnamese Communists.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.59,2:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这点  你们美国人永远不会明白\N{\rEng}And this is something that you never understood, you American.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.39,2:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  或许将来\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.53,2:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会与越盟和解\N{\rEng}Maybe in the future we can make something with the Vietminh.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.06,2:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白吗？\N{\rEng}Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.13,2:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,越共说  走开  走开\N{\rEng}The VC say, ''Go away. Go away.''
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.07,2:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所有白人  都无法呆在印度支那\N{\rEng}That's fiInish for all the white people in Indochina.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.71,2:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,法国人和美国人并无分别\N{\rEng}If you're French, American, that's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.21,2:07:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  他们想忘掉你们\N{\rEng}''Go.'' They want to forget you.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.21,2:07:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  上尉\N{\rEng}Look, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.95,2:07:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是事实\N{\rEng}Look,this is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.18,2:07:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一只鸡蛋\N{\rEng}An egg.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.85,2:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋白流走\N{\rEng}The white left...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.64,2:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可蛋黄仍在\N{\rEng}but the yellow stays!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.68,2:07:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我在西贡时  跟一个美国政客谈过\N{\rEng}When I was in Saigon, I spoke to an American politician.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.69,2:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他解释得很好  他说：\N{\rEng}He explained it very well. He said, ''Look.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.82,2:07:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  昨天是朝鲜  今天是越南\N{\rEng}Yesterday, it was korea. Today, Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.04,2:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是泰国  菲律宾\N{\rEng}Tomorrow, Thailand, the Philippines...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.58,2:08:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,之后  可能是欧洲\N{\rEng}then maybe Europe.''
Dialogue: 0,2:08:05.38,2:08:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不会是欧洲？\N{\rEng}Come on. Why not Europe?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:06.52,2:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看看捷克斯洛伐克  最近发生的\N{\rEng}Look what happened in Czechoslovakia recently.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.12,2:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至在二战前\N{\rEng}Even before Second World War
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.82,2:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,美国人就知道了  要发生什么事\N{\rEng}Americans knew exactly what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:12.96,2:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不想那混蛋接管\N{\rEng}They don't want that shit to take over! LeFevre!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.18,2:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们白人都是混蛋\N{\rEng}All you white people are shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.75,2:08:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在为自由抗争\N{\rEng}They are fiIghting--fiIghting for freedom.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.12,2:08:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,自由？  胡扯\N{\rEng}Freedom? Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:25.32,2:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,法国人胡话  美国人胡话\N{\rEng}French bullshit. American bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.52,2:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,奠边府的陷阱\N{\rEng}Dien Bien Phu, that serious.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.03,2:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所有士兵  都知道他们已经完了\N{\rEng}All soldiers know they are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:36.27,2:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道奠边府战役吗？\N{\rEng}You know anything about Dien Bien Phu?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.30,2:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道  -不  你不知道\N{\rEng}-Yeah, I know.  -No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:44.24,2:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不真的知道\N{\rEng}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:45.41,2:08:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,奠边府是个错误  一个军事错误\N{\rEng}Dien Bien Phu was an error.A military mistake.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.61,2:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,错误？  是个故意的错误！\N{\rEng}A mistake? A voluntary mistake!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.08,2:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,故意的！\N{\rEng}Voluntary!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.72,2:08:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有士兵都知道\N{\rEng}All the soldiers knew.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:57.22,2:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道自己会死\N{\rEng}We knew we would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.92,2:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那些将军和上校以为\N{\rEng}The generals and the colonels believe it's impossible for the Viets...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:00.76,2:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,越南人不可能运大炮上山\N{\rEng}to get the cannon up there in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:04.73,2:09:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们办到了\N{\rEng}But they do.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.43,2:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后等着下雨\N{\rEng}Then they wait for the rain to come.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.32,2:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,雨下起来后  没有飞机能到那\N{\rEng}When it comes, no airplane can fly there.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.82,2:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的伞兵  从90米高往下跳下\N{\rEng}And our paratroopers jump at 90 meters.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:17.66,2:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,90米  70米\N{\rEng}I mean, you know, 90 meters--70 meters.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.33,2:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是发疯\N{\rEng}I mean, that's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.96,2:09:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没哪支军队会那样干\N{\rEng}No army in the world can do that.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.20,2:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只想跟朋友们死在一起\N{\rEng}And they only do that to be dead with their friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.94,2:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,法国军队被牺牲了\N{\rEng}The French Army was sacrifiIced.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.38,2:09:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,被安安稳稳在家的政客们牺牲了\N{\rEng}SacrifiIced by the politicians safe at home.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.15,2:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把军队推入了\N{\rEng}They put the army in an impossible situation
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.71,2:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能取胜的境地\N{\rEng}where they couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.12,2:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,学生们在巴黎游行示威\N{\rEng}The students are marching in Paris protesting, demonstrating.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.65,2:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,从背后捅了士兵们一刀\N{\rEng}They stab the soldiers in their back.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:48.89,2:09:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,士兵要拉响手雷\N{\rEng}The soldier would open the grenade,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.42,2:09:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它却不会爆炸\N{\rEng}it wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.93,2:09:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一张字条掉了出来\N{\rEng}A piece of paper would fall--
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.20,2:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,法国妇女联盟  我们支持越南\N{\rEng}''Union of French Women.'' ''We are for the Viets.''
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.70,2:10:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,叛徒！ 国内的共产党叛徒\N{\rEng}Traitors! Communist traitors at home.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.07,2:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是奠边府\N{\rEng}Dien Bien Phu, okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.24,2:10:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,法国人是混蛋\N{\rEng}The French is shit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.68,2:10:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没人关心  没人想要\N{\rEng}No one care. No one want--
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.52,2:10:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们美国人为何\N{\rEng}Why don't you Americans learn from us,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.50,2:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不从我们的错误中学乖？\N{\rEng}from our mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.34,2:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,依你们的军队  你们的实力\N{\rEng}Mon Dieux, with your army, your strength your power,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.12,2:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你们想就能赢！\N{\rEng}you could win if you want to!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.21,2:10:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能赢\N{\rEng}You can win.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.15,2:10:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定我们能在这有所作为\N{\rEng}You know, I'm sure we can make something here.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.65,2:10:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定\N{\rEng}I'm sure about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:38.82,2:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不亏待这里的人\N{\rEng}I never do something wrong to the people here.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.96,2:10:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEng}That's right,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.86,2:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可国内的共产党从没背叛\N{\rEng}but the Communist at home have never been traitors.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:21.03,2:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安  上尉\N{\rEng}Capitaine, good night.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.20,2:11:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个社会主义者\N{\rEng}He was a Socialist, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.40,2:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们能留下\N{\rEng}I know that we can stay.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.80,2:11:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们能留下并开创事业\N{\rEng}I know that we can stay.We can.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.51,2:11:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们经常帮越南人\N{\rEng}You know, we always helped the people.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.13,2:11:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他们一起干活\N{\rEng}We work with the people.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.80,2:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们  可以推断自己是受欢迎的\N{\rEng}So we can be friends, we are agreed.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:54.33,2:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  上尉  我的祖父\N{\rEng}See, Captain, when my grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.90,2:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,和叔父刚来时\N{\rEng}and my uncle's father came here...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:04.81,2:12:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这里一片荒芜\N{\rEng}there was nothing--nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.74,2:12:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,越南什么也不是\N{\rEng}The Vietnamese were nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.92,2:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我们非常努力地工作\N{\rEng}So we worked hard...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.79,2:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,从巴西运来橡胶树\N{\rEng}the rubber from Brazil,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:19.69,2:12:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,种植在这里\N{\rEng}and then plant it here.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.39,2:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们雇用越南人  和他们一起干活\N{\rEng}We took the Vietnamese, work with them...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:28.33,2:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,从无到有\N{\rEng}make something--something out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.93,2:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你问我为何我们想留下  上尉\N{\rEng}So when you ask me why we want to stay here, Captain...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.21,2:12:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想留下  因为这地方是我们的\N{\rEng}we want to stay here because it's ours
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.68,2:12:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它属于我们  令我们的家人团结\N{\rEng}it belongs to us.It keeps our family together.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:45.21,2:12:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为此而战\N{\rEng}I mean, we fiIght for that.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:49.20,2:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们美国人\N{\rEng}While you Americans, you are fiIghting for...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.74,2:12:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,却为史上最虚无的东西而战\N{\rEng}the biggest nothing in history.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:04.58,2:13:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  上尉\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:07.02,2:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去看看你们的人\N{\rEng}I will see if your men need any help
Dialogue: 0,2:13:09.37,2:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是否需要东西修船\N{\rEng}to repair your boat...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.92,2:13:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好继续你们的战争\N{\rEng}so that you can go on with your war.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.61,2:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我为我的家人向你道歉  上尉\N{\rEng}I apologize for my family, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.22,2:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都在这里失去了很多\N{\rEng}We have all lost much here.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.72,2:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,赫伯特失去了妻子和两个孩子\N{\rEng}Hubert--his wife and two sons.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:06.41,2:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去了丈夫\N{\rEng}And I have lost a husband.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.29,2:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\rEng}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:16.29,2:14:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你厌倦了战争\N{\rEng}You are tired of the war.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:20.49,2:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我能从你脸上看出来\N{\rEng}I can see it in your face.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.10,2:14:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和法国士兵眼神里的一个样\N{\rEng}'Twas the same in the eyes of the soldiers of our war.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:30.84,2:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们称他们为\N{\rEng}We called them ''Les Soldats Perdus--''
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.67,2:14:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,迷失的士兵\N{\rEng}The Lost Soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.30,2:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意  我们可以来点科纳克白兰地\N{\rEng}If you like, we can have some cognac.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.60,2:14:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不了\N{\rEng}No.I...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.14,2:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去找我的部下  而且\N{\rEng}I have to--to see about my men and--
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.43,2:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,明天  这里还会有战争\N{\rEng}The war will be still here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.75,2:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我想你是对的\N{\rEng}Yeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.86,2:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我注意到你晚餐时没喝酒\N{\rEng}I noticed you had no wine at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.69,2:15:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喝酒\N{\rEng}No, I don't drink wine.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:34.83,2:15:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是喜欢科纳克\N{\rEng}I do like cognac,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:37.36,2:15:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在不想喝  谢谢\N{\rEng}but I don't want any now. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:40.11,2:15:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:42.94,2:15:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我只好一个人喝了\N{\rEng}then I--I must drink alone.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:56.10,2:15:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你战后会回美国吗？\N{\rEng}Will you go back after the war to America?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.58,2:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:04.98,2:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那你跟我们一样  家就在这\N{\rEng}Then you're like us--your home is here.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:25.95,2:16:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道人为什么\N{\rEng}Do you know why you can never step
Dialogue: 0,2:16:28.10,2:16:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不能两次踏入同一条河流吗？\N{\rEng}into the same river twice?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:32.12,2:16:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,知道  因为它总在流动\N{\rEng}Yeah. 'Cause it's always moving.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.63,2:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前常为丈夫准备一管\N{\rEng}I used to prepare a pipe for my husband.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:47.02,2:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他心脏受伤  要靠吗啡止痛\N{\rEng}'Twas the morphine he took for the wounds he suffered in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:54.93,2:16:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我那迷失的士兵  会大吵大嚷\N{\rEng}He would rage and he would cry, my lost soldier.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:02.37,2:17:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我对他说\N{\rEng}And I said to him,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.16,2:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不到有两个你吗？\N{\rEng}There are two of you.Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:09.26,2:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一个杀人  一个爱人\N{\rEng}One that kills and one that loves.''
Dialogue: 0,2:17:15.07,2:17:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他对我说\N{\rEng}And he said to me...
Dialogue: 0,2:17:17.57,2:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不晓得自己  是畜生还是神\N{\rEng}''I don't know whether I'm an animal or a god.''
Dialogue: 0,2:17:24.73,2:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但你两者皆是\N{\rEng}But you are both.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:08.45,2:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还要吗？\N{\rEng}You want more?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:15.69,2:18:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是  你还活着\N{\rEng}All that matters is that you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:21.17,2:18:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你还活着  上尉\N{\rEng}You are alive, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:27.44,2:18:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是真相\N{\rEng}That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.86,2:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不到有两个你吗？\N{\rEng}There are two of you, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:47.70,2:19:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一个杀人  一个爱人\N{\rEng}One that kills...and one that loves.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:21.22,2:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也看不见  停下\N{\rEng}Can't see nothing. We stoppin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:24.32,2:20:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你无权停船  酋长\N{\rEng}You're not authorized to stop this boat, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.81,2:20:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了什么也看不见\N{\rEng}I said I can't see a thing,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.49,2:20:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉！ 我要停船\N{\rEng}Captain. I'm stopping this boat.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.38,2:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再拿任何人冒险\N{\rEng}I ain't riskin' no more lives.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:31.98,2:20:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这里由我指挥  妈的\N{\rEng}I'm in command here, goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:33.74,2:20:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你要听我的\N{\rEng}You'll do what I say.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.09,2:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见什么了吗  大厨？\N{\rEng}You see anything, Chef?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:41.26,2:20:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么不他妈的攻击？\N{\rEng}Why don't they fucking attack, man?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.71,2:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小心这  酋长\N{\rEng}Watch it over here, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.08,2:21:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有截断树桩\N{\rEng}Got a stump.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.65,2:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  上50口径机枪\N{\rEng}Lance,On the fiIfties.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:12.32,2:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他在附近\N{\rEng}He was close.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:16.09,2:21:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,相当近\N{\rEng}He was real close.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:20.06,2:21:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然看不见他  但却能感觉到\N{\rEng}I couldn't see him yet, but I could feel him...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:23.03,2:21:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就像船只被卷入上游\N{\rEng}as if the boat were being sucked upriver...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:25.07,2:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而河水会流回丛林\N{\rEng}and the water was flowing backinto thejungle.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.51,2:21:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何\N{\rEng}Whatever was going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:33.14,2:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都和他们在老川\N{\rEng}it wasn't going to be the way
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.02,2:21:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,形容的有天壤之别\N{\rEng}they called it backin Nha Trang.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.51,2:21:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-有箭！  -开火！\N{\rEng}-Arrows!  -Fire!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.39,2:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨  开火！\N{\rEng}Chef, open up! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:52.73,2:21:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨  开火！\N{\rEng}Lance, fiIre!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:02.70,2:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨！ 没事了  停火\N{\rEng}Chef! Chef, it's okay. Quit fiIring.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:06.37,2:22:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只是玩具箭\N{\rEng}They're just little toy arrows.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.97,2:22:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！ 安静！\N{\rEng}Cut it out! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.18,2:22:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,酋长  叫他们停火！\N{\rEng}Chief, tell them to hold their fiIre!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:12.95,2:22:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是小树枝\N{\rEng}They're just little sticks.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:14.31,2:22:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,想吓唬我们\N{\rEng}They're just trying to scare us.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:15.88,2:22:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,安静！\N{\rEng}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.15,2:22:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我们陷入狼狈\N{\rEng}You got us into this mess,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:19.35,2:22:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在却无计可施\N{\rEng}and now you can't get us out...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:20.85,2:22:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你也不知道究竟要去哪  是吧？\N{\rEng}You got us into this mess, and now you can't get us out...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:23.56,2:22:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧？\N{\rEng}Do ya?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:25.69,2:22:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋！\N{\rEng}You son of a bitch! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:30.50,2:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  来开船！\N{\rEng}Lance, get the wheel!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:33.23,2:22:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些野蛮人  来尝尝吧！ 你这混蛋！\N{\rEng}You savages! Come and get it! You son of a bitches!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.26,2:22:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一支长矛\N{\rEng}A spear?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:18.37,2:24:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任务是进柬埔寨\N{\rEng}My mission is to make it up into Cambodia.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:21.77,2:24:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在那  有个绿色贝雷帽的上校疯了\N{\rEng}There's a Green Beret colonel up there who's gone insane...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:24.54,2:24:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去处决他\N{\rEng}and I'm supposed to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:27.68,2:24:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真有种！\N{\rEng}That's fucking typical! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:30.68,2:24:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的越南任务\N{\rEng}Fuckin' Vietnam mission!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:32.95,2:24:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须去那\N{\rEng}I'm short and we gotta go up there
Dialogue: 0,2:24:34.72,2:24:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好让你杀个自己人？\N{\rEng}so you can kill one of our own guys?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:36.69,2:24:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈的好！\N{\rEng}That's fucking great!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:41.46,2:24:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈的发疯\N{\rEng}Shit! That's fuckin' crazy.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:44.80,2:24:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你要去炸座桥\N{\rEng}I mean, I thought you were going in to blow up a bridge...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:47.90,2:24:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,或铁路之类的\N{\rEng}or some fuckin' railroad tracks or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:51.74,2:24:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-对不起  -不  等等\N{\rEng}-That's all right.  -No. No, wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:54.01,2:24:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起坐船去\N{\rEng}We'll go together, on the boat. We'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:57.34,2:25:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一起坐船去  好吗？\N{\rEng}We'll go up there, but on the boat. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:07.95,2:26:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我对到那后\N{\rEng}Part of me was afraid of what I would find...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:10.05,2:26:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,会发现和要做的事  有点恐惧\N{\rEng}and what I would do when I got there.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:14.99,2:26:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道有危险\N{\rEng}I knew the risks...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:17.82,2:26:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,或假装自己知道\N{\rEng}or imagined I knew.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:21.96,2:26:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但比恐惧感觉更强烈的\N{\rEng}But the thing I felt the most...much stronger than fear...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.83,2:26:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是渴望面对他\N{\rEng}was the desire to confront him.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:42.44,2:27:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,继续前进\N{\rEng}Just keep movin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:44.58,2:27:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  手离枪远点\N{\rEng}Lance, keep your hands away from the guns.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:14.90,2:29:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没事！ 允许你们进来了！\N{\rEng}It's all right! It's all right! It's all been approved!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:19.23,2:29:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不进去！ 那些混蛋会袭击我们！\N{\rEng}I ain't comin' in there! Them bastards attacked us!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:23.27,2:29:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,用汽笛吓跑他们！\N{\rEng}Hey, zap 'em with your siren, man. Zap 'em with your siren.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:37.55,2:29:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那有水雷！ 那也有！\N{\rEng}There's mines over there and mines over there too.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.65,2:29:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小心  那些该死的猴子会咬人\N{\rEng}And watch out. Those goddamn monkeys will bite you, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:43.02,2:29:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错  朝着我开\N{\rEng}Ah, that's a pretty one. Move it right in towards me.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:46.79,2:29:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是美国人！ 美国平民\N{\rEng}I'm an American.Yeah. An American civilian.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:49.96,2:29:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  美国佬\N{\rEng}Hi, Yanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:51.47,2:29:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,美国平民  没事了\N{\rEng}Hi. American.American civilian. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:55.70,2:29:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你有我梦寐以求的香烟\N{\rEng}And you got the cigarettes. And that's what I've been dreaming about.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:59.71,2:30:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大厨\N{\rEng}Chelf.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:01.44,2:30:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\rEng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:03.38,2:30:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你又是谁？\N{\rEng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:08.48,2:30:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个摄影记者\N{\rEng}I'm a photojournalist.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:10.78,2:30:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我自64年起  就负责报道这场战争\N{\rEng}I've covered the war since '64.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:13.15,2:30:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去过老挝  柬埔寨和越南\N{\rEng}I've been in Laos, Cambodia and 'Nam.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.33,2:30:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说  这船一团糟\N{\rEng}Hoo-wee, baby. I'll tell you one thing. This boat is a mess, man.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:24.10,2:30:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是什么人？\N{\rEng}Who are all these people?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:25.60,2:30:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为你是来\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, they think you've come to--
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.77,2:30:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,带他走的  希望不是这样\N{\rEng}to take him away.And I hope that isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:32.91,2:30:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,带谁走？\N{\rEng}Take who away?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:36.11,2:30:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他呀  库上校！\N{\rEng}Him! Col. kurtz.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:39.81,2:30:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看见的  都是他的子民\N{\rEng}These are all his children, man, as far as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:43.58,2:30:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的人全是他的子民\N{\rEng}Hell, man, out here we're all his children.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:47.32,2:30:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能跟库上校谈谈吗？\N{\rEng}Could we talk to Col. kurtz?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:51.13,2:30:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是跟上校谈\N{\rEng}Hey, mac. You don't talk to the colonel.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:55.50,2:30:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而是听他说\N{\rEng}Well, you listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:58.47,2:31:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他启发我们\N{\rEng}The man's enlarged my mind.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:01.27,2:31:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在传统意义上  他是个诗人战土\N{\rEng}He's a poet warrior in the classic sense.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:04.77,2:31:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说  有时他    你向他问好\N{\rEng}I mean, sometimes he'll--Well, you say hello to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:07.71,2:31:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他会走过你身旁  却对你视若无睹\N{\rEng}He'll just walk by you and he won't even notice you.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:10.71,2:31:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,突然又会抓住你\N{\rEng}Then suddenly he'll grab you
Dialogue: 0,2:31:12.21,2:31:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,带到一个角落  说\N{\rEng}and he'll throw you in a corner and he'll say...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:14.35,2:31:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道生命中充满假如？\N{\rEng}''Do you know that 'if' is the middle word in 'life'?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:16.72,2:31:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,假如所有的人都失去理智并指责你\N{\rEng}If you can keep your head
Dialogue: 0,2:31:17.98,2:31:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而你仍保持清醒\N{\rEng}when all about you are losing theirs and blaming you.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:19.35,2:31:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,假如所有的人都怀疑你  而你仍能相信自己\N{\rEng}If you can trust yourself when all men doubt you.''
Dialogue: 0,2:31:21.36,2:31:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能  我是小人物  他是个伟人\N{\rEng}I'm a little man. I'm a little man. He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:25.19,2:31:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿有一对锯齿状的爪\N{\rEng}''I should have been a pair of ragged claws...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:28.93,2:31:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好划破沉默的海底\N{\rEng}scuttling across floors of silent seas.''
Dialogue: 0,2:31:31.17,2:31:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是说  -留在船上\N{\rEng}-I mean--  -Stay with the boat.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.37,2:31:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别丢下我  好吗？\N{\rEng}Don't go any--Don't go without me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:36.00,2:31:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要拍照\N{\rEng}I wanna get a picture.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:39.67,2:31:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他有时很可怕  有时很普通\N{\rEng}He can be terrible and he can be mean...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:43.44,2:31:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能是对的\N{\rEng}and he can be right.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:45.31,2:31:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他在战斗\N{\rEng}He's fiIghting the war.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:47.48,2:31:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个伟人\N{\rEng}He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:51.62,2:31:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\rEng}I mean--
Dialogue: 0,2:31:56.22,2:31:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望能用语言来形容\N{\rEng}I wish I had words, you know. I wish I had words.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:59.86,2:32:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以告诉你  前几天他想杀我\N{\rEng}I could tell you something like, the other day he wanted to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:03.10,2:32:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,诸如此类\N{\rEng}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:04.33,2:32:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么想杀你？\N{\rEng}Why'd he want to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:06.10,2:32:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我拍了他的照片\N{\rEng}Because I took his picture.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:08.40,2:32:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他说  你要是再拍我\N{\rEng}He said, ''If you take my picture again...
Dialogue: 0,2:32:12.11,2:32:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我就宰了你\N{\rEng}I'm gonna kill you.''
Dialogue: 0,2:32:14.51,2:32:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他是认真的\N{\rEng}And he meant it.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:18.38,2:32:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你得保持冷静  懂吗？\N{\rEng}See, just lay cool. Lay cool.Lay back. Dig it.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:22.95,2:32:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他又友善了  确实如此\N{\rEng}He gets friendly again. He really does.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:26.32,2:32:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但你无法猜度上校\N{\rEng}But you don't--you don't--you don't judge the colonel.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:29.82,2:32:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能用正常人的尺度猜度他\N{\rEng}You don't judge the colonel like an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:38.60,2:32:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  看着  这些是美国人！ 美国人\N{\rEng}Okay, watch it now. These are Americans. Americans!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:42.40,2:32:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好好感受这个地方\N{\rEng}You can feel the vibe of this place.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:44.81,2:32:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,让我给你拍照\N{\rEng}Let me take your picture.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:46.14,2:32:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你能停  ？  嗨！ 嗨！\N{\rEng}Hey, could you hold--Hey, hello. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:48.21,2:32:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你能停一下吗？\N{\rEng}Could you hold up a minute?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:12.17,2:33:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,科比\N{\rEng}Colby.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:29.72,2:33:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那些头\N{\rEng}The heads.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:31.89,2:33:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你在看那些头\N{\rEng}You're looking at the heads.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:35.56,2:33:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有时他做过了火\N{\rEng}I, uh--Sometimes he goes too far.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:38.13,2:33:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,会第一个站出来承认\N{\rEng}He's the fiIrst one to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:40.89,2:33:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-他疯了  -不对！\N{\rEng}-He's gone crazy.  -Wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:45.17,2:33:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你早到两天\N{\rEng}If you could have heard the man just two days ago--
Dialogue: 0,2:33:48.10,2:33:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,听了他的讲话\N{\rEng}if you could have heard him then, God--
Dialogue: 0,2:33:50.87,2:33:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-你还会说他疯了？  -绝对是\N{\rEng}-You were gonna call him crazy?  -Fuckin' A!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:56.14,2:33:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想跟他谈谈\N{\rEng}I just wanna talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:59.88,2:34:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  他已经走了\N{\rEng}Well, man, he's gone away.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:03.28,2:34:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他和部下一起\N{\rEng}He's gone away.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:04.63,2:34:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,消失在了丛林中\N{\rEng}He disappeared out in the jungle with his people.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:06.15,2:34:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我会等他\N{\rEng}I'll wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:07.67,2:34:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他和部下在一起  感觉自在\N{\rEng}He feels comfortable with his people.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:09.39,2:34:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他们在一起  他忘了自己\N{\rEng}He forgets himself with his people.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:13.56,2:34:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他忘了自己\N{\rEng}He forgets himself.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:15.13,2:34:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉？\N{\rEng}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:16.50,2:34:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该回船上等\N{\rEng}Maybe we should wait back at the boat.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:19.47,2:34:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-我认为你  -好的  大厨\N{\rEng}-I think you should-- -Okay, Chef.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:21.40,2:34:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要回船上一会\N{\rEng}We'll go back to the boat for a while.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.47,2:34:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  陪着兰斯\N{\rEng}Yeah, stay with Lance.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:48.83,2:34:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这上校是个疯子\N{\rEng}This colonel guy, he's wacko, man.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:52.03,2:34:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,比疯掉还糟  他是恶魔\N{\rEng}He's worse than crazy. He's evil!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:54.77,2:34:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他因之自命不凡的\N{\rEng}I mean, that's what the man's got set up here, man!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:57.27,2:34:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的异教偶像崇拜！ 看看四周\N{\rEng}It's fuckin' pagan idolatry. Look around you!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:01.12,2:35:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-妈的  他是个疯子  -那你会帮我吗？\N{\rEng}-Shit, he's loco.  -Then you'll help me?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:04.19,2:35:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙？ 当然  为了从这摊烂事中脱身\N{\rEng}Fuckin' A, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:05.83,2:35:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我会做任何事\N{\rEng}I'll do anything to get out of this joint.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:07.76,2:35:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\rEng}Good boy.
